tice%20(ICJ)%20in%20The%20Hague%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20African%20countries%20should%20support%20South%20Africa%20in%20this%20step%2C%E2%80%9D%20Modou%20Jawo%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20the%20Gambian%20capital%2C%20Banjul%2C%20told%20DW.%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20Israel%20is%20doing%20is%20killing%20innocent%20people.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESouth%20Africa%E2%80%99s%20case%20against%20Israel%20at%20the%20ICJ%20is%20one%20of%20three%20currently%20before%20the%20top%20United%20Nations%20(UN)%20court%2C%20often%20described%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9CWorld%20Court.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20cases%20include%20one%20that%20was%20filed%20by%20Ukraine%20shortly%20after%20Russia%E2%80%99s%20invasion%2C%20accusing%20Moscow%20of%20launching%20the%20military%20operation%20based%20on%20trumped-up%20claims%20of%20genocide%2C%20and%20in%20turn%20accusing%20Russia%20of%20planning%20acts%20of%20genocide%20in%20Ukraine%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELastly%2C%20in%20November%202019%2C%20Gambia%20filed%20a%20case%20at%20the%20ICJ%20on%20behalf%20of%20Muslim%20nations.%20It%20accuses%20Myanmar%20of%20genocide%20against%20the%20Rohingya%20Muslim%20minority.%20Gambia%20is%20predominantly%20Muslim%20and%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Organisation%20of%20Islamic%20Cooperation%20(OIC)%2C%20which%20boasts%20about%2030%20African%20member%20states%20and%20is%20backing%20South%20Africa%E2%80%99s%20case%20against%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202020%2C%20during%20an%20early%20stage%20of%20proceedings%2C%20the%20ICJ%20ruled%20in%20favour%20of%20Gambia%2C%20ordering%20Myanmar%20to%20%E2%80%9Ctake%20all%20measures%20within%20its%20power%E2%80%9D%20to%20prevent%20the%20commission%20of%20acts%20defined%20in%20the%20convention%20%E2%80%93%20including%20ensuring%20that%20its%20military%20and%20any%20irregular%20armed%20units%20refrain%20from%20committing%20such%20acts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20do%20the%20South%20African%20and%20Gambian%20cases%20differ%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSouth%20Africa%E2%80%99s%20motivations%20might%20be%20very%20different%20from%20The%20Gambia%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Thijs%20Bouwgnegt%2C%20senior%20researcher%20at%20the%20NIOD%20Institute%20for%20War%2C%20Holocaust%20and%20Genocide%20Studies%20in%20Amsterdam%2C%20adding%20that%20South%20Africa%E2%80%99s%20record%20of%2046%20years%20of%20legislated%20apartheid%20might%20have%20played%20a%20vital%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%2084-page%20application%2C%20South%20Africa%20stresses%20some%20similarities%20they%20see%20with%20the%20Palestinian%20territories.%20Israel%20rejects%20any%20suggestions%20of%20similarities%20with%20apartheid%2C%20and%20the%20claim%20is%20highly%20contentious%20globally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20a%20very%20good%20move%20because%20it%20reflects%20South%20Africa%E2%80%99s%20commitment%20to%20advocating%20for%20human%20rights%20and%20supporting%20those%20affected%20by%20conflict%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dija%20Jawo%2C%20a%20Gambian%20blogger%2C%20told%20DW.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJawo%20also%20said%20that%20the%20rights%20of%20those%20living%20through%20apartheid%20in%20South%20Africa%20were%20violated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSome%20were%20killed%2C%20and%20some%20were%20imprisoned%20like%20Nelson%20Mandela%20for%20over%20two%20decades.%20So%20they%20know%20what%20the%20Gazans%20are%20going%20through%2C%E2%80%9D%20claimed%20Jawo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJewish%20South%20Africans%20are%20disappointed%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20South%20African%20Jewish%20Board%20of%20Deputies%20(SAJBD)%20has%20criticised%20the%20South%20African%20government%20for%20taking%20Israel%20to%20the%20ICJ.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20not%20seen%20this%20being%20done%20by%20South%20Africa%20in%20relation%20to%20the%20Russia-Ukraine%20conflict%2C%20in%20relation%20to%20horrific%20conflicts%20occurring%20throughout%20Africa%2C%20including%20at%20the%20moment%20in%20the%20Congo%20and%20in%20the%20Sudan%2C%E2%80%9D%20Karen%20Milner%2C%20the%20national%20chair%20of%20the%20SAJBD%2C%20told%20DW.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESouth%20Africa%E2%80%99s%20case%20arose%20after%20Israel%20launched%20its%20offensive%20in%20Gaza%20after%20Hamas%20%E2%80%93%20which%20has%20been%20recognised%20as%20a%20terrorist%20group%20by%20the%20EU%2C%20the%20United%20States%2C%20Germany%20and%20others%2C%20but%20not%20South%20Africa%20%E2%80%93%20carried%20out%20a%20series%20of%20major%20terror%20attacks%20in%20southern%20Israel%20on%20October%207%2C%20killing%20some%201%2C200%20people%20and%20taking%20more%20than%20200%20hostages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETens%20of%20thousands%20of%20Palestinians%20in%20Gaza%20have%20since%20been%20killed%20in%20the%20fighting%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Hamas-run%20Health%20Ministry%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20Nations%20has%20warned%20that%20the%20humanitarian%20situation%20in%20Gaza%20is%20deteriorating.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSouth%20Africa%20could%20have%20chosen%20a%20route%20which%20would%20have%20led%20to%20peace%2C%E2%80%9D%20Milner%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20stressed%20that%20South%20Africa%20could%20have%20specifically%20demanded%20and%20placed%20pressure%20on%20Hamas%20to%20release%20the%20hostages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CInstead%2C%20they%20have%20engaged%20in%20an%20extremely%20expensive%2C%20extensive%20legal%20process%20which%20is%20unlikely%20to%20have%20any%20real%20impact%20ultimately%20on%20the%20conclusion%20of%20this%20war.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E1948%20UN%20Genocide%20Convention%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20complaint%20filed%20at%20the%20ICJ%2C%20South%20Africa%20invoked%20the%201948%20UN%20Convention%20on%20the%20Prevention%20and%20punishment%20of%20the%20Crime%20of%20Genocide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20crime%20of%20genocide%20under%20international%20law%20means%20specific%20acts%20done%20with%20the%20intent%20to%20destroy%20members%20of%20a%20national%2C%20racial%2C%20ethnic%2C%20or%20religious%20group.%20As%20such%2C%20in%20whole%20or%20in%20part%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bouwgnegt%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20has%20firmly%20rejected%20the%20genocide%20allegations%20and%20vowed%20to%20fight%20them%20at%20the%20ICJ.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%2C%20President%20Isaac%20Herzog%2C%20and%20other%20senior%20Israeli%20officials%20have%20made%20strong%20public%20statements%20accusing%20South%20Africa%20of%20%E2%80%9Cblood%20libel%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20or%20antisemitism%20%E2%80%93%20the%20term%20for%20hostility%20or%20prejudice%20against%20Jewish%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addressing%20the%20opening%20hearing%20at%20the%20ICJ%20on%20Thursday%2C%20South%20African%20advocate%20Tembeka%20Ngcukaitobi%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9CIsrael%20has%20a%20genocidal%20intent%20against%20the%20Palestinians%20in%20Gaza.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%E2%80%99s%20legal%20representatives%20are%20due%20to%20address%20the%20ICJ%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDW%20asked%20Michael%20Becker%2C%20Assistant%20Professor%20of%20International%20Human%20Rights%20Law%20at%20Trinity%20College%20Dublin%2C%20about%20the%20allegation%20of%20%E2%80%9Cgenocidal%20intent.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20very%20difficult%20to%20establish%20what%E2%80%99s%20referred%20to%20as%20genocidal%20intent%2C%E2%80%9D%20Becker%20said.%20%E2%80%9CThat%20question%20of%20whether%20the%20requisite%20level%20of%20intent%20is%20present%20is%20difficult%20to%20show%20in%20a%20court%20of%20law.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20Becker%20and%20Bouwgnegt%20agree%20that%20establishing%20whether%20or%20not%20Israel%20has%20committed%20or%20is%20committing%20genocide%20was%20a%20difficult%20question%20that%20could%20take%20many%20years%20to%20answer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20one%20of%20the%20most%20challenging%20crimes%20to%20prove%20in%20a%20court%20of%20law%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bouwgnegt%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhy%20is%20South%20Africa%20taking%20Israel%20to%20court%20for%20genocide%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESankulleh%20Janko%20(in%20Banjul)%2C%20Thuso%20Khumalo%20(in%20Johannesburg)%20and%20Lucia%20Schulten%20(in%20The%20Hague)%20contributed%20to%20this%20article.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20first%20appeared%20on%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fsouth-africas-case-against-israel-divides-opinion-in-africa%2Fa-67954312%5C%22%3EDW%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705043993000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F12124738%2FGDlGaaIXsAAaSIJ.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fsouth-africas-case-against-israel-divides-opinion-in-africa%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Proceedings%20have%20opened%20at%20the%20International%20Court%20of%20Justice%20(ICJ)%2C%20where%20South%20Africa%20accuses%20Israel%20of%20'genocidal%20acts'%20in%20Gaza.%20Analysts%20say%20the%20case%20could%20drag%20on%20for%20years.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fsouth-africas-case-against-israel-divides-opinion-in-africa%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sunil%20Kanugolu%2C%20Key%20To%20Congress%20Telangana%20Win%2C%20Not%20Part%20of%202024%20Planning%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fsunil-kanugolu%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESunil%20Kanugolu%3C%2Fa%3E%20-%20the%20strategist%20credited%20with%20orchestrating%20the%20Congress'%20wins%20in%20Karnataka%20and%20Telangana%20-%20will%20not%20be%20part%20of%20its%20campaign%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2F2024-lok-sabha-election%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2024%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Earlier%20part%20of%20the%20Congress'%20'Task%20Force%202024'%2C%20he%20will%20now%20focus%20on%20prepping%20the%20party's%20Haryana%20and%20Maharashtra%20campaigns%2C%20sources%20close%20to%20him%20told%20NDTV%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kanugolu's%20redeployment%20has%20been%20attributed%20to%20the%20fact%20he%20already%20has%20teams%20in%20place%20in%20those%20two%20states%20-%20both%20of%20which%20will%20vote%20within%20seven%20months%20-%20and%20to%20a%20Congress%20keen%20to%20build%20on%20last%20year's%20victories%20in%20the%20Karnataka%20and%20Telangana%20Assembly%20elections%2C%20recording%20big%20wins%20over%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20and%20BRS%2C%20respectively.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20news%20the%20Congress'%20key%20poll%20tactician%20will%20not%20be%20on%20hand%20to%20guide%20the%20party%20in%20the%20April%2FMay%20national%20election%20has%20raised%20eyebrows.%20A%20senior%20leader%2C%20holding%20the%20rank%20of%20General%20Secretary%2C%20acknowledged%20his%20absence%20on%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20campaign%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bslight%20setback%26quot%3B%2C%20but%20told%20NDTV%20the%20Congress%20believes%20there%20is%20greater%20long-term%20benefit%20if%20he%20can%20use%20his%20'Midas%20touch'%2C%20to%20win%20key%20states%20from%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kanugolu%2C%20sources%20added%2C%20will%20also%20continue%20to%20work%20with%20the%20Congress'%20governments%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20where%20he%20his%20now%20Chief%20Minister%20Siddaramaiah's%20primary%20advisor%2C%20with%20a%20cabinet%20rank%2C%20and%20Telangana%2C%20where%20he%20ousted%20ex-Chief%20Minister%20K%20Chandrashekar%20Rao%20and%20the%20BRS%20that%20has%20ruled%20since%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fkarnataka-news%2Fcongresss-poll-strategist-sunil-kanugolu-is-now-chief-advisor-to-karnataka-chief-minister-4084480%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECongress'%20Poll%20Planner%20Now%20Chief%20Advisor%20To%20Karnataka%20Chief%20Minister%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20importance%20of%20Mr%20Kanugolu%20to%20the%20Congress'%20election%20machinery%20is%20perhaps%20best%20illustrated%20by%20the%20party's%20dismal%20performances%20in%20last%20year's%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Rajasthan%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fkarnataka-news%2Fsunil-kanugolu-the-data-driven-strategist-behind-congresss-karnataka-win-4033493%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESunil%20Kanugolu%2C%20Data-Driven%20Strategist%20Behind%20Congress'%20Karnataka%20Win%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kanugolu%20held%20initial%20talks%20with%20leaders%20in%20those%20states%2C%20but%20neither%20Kamal%20Nath%20nor%20Ashok%20Gehlot%2C%20the%20party's%20oldest%20and%20de%20facto%20bosses%20in%20each%2C%20agreed%20to%20his%20demands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftelangana-news%2Fsunil-kanugolu-congress-telangana-strategist-was-snubbed-in-rajasthan-madhya-pradesh-4630893%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECongress'%20Telangana%20Strategist%20Snubbed%20In%20Rajasthan%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20lost%20badly%20in%20each%20state.%20Sources%20later%20told%20NDTV%20the%20wins%20in%20Karnataka%20and%20Telangana%20were%20the%20result%20of%20Mr%20Kanugolu%20being%20given%20a%20free%20hand%20in%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20math%20behind%20the%20Congress'%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20campaign%20is%20significantly%20more%20complicated%2C%20particularly%20with%20the%20party%20juggling%20multiple%20allies%2C%20and%20seat-sharing%20demands%2C%20as%20part%20of%20the%20INDIA%20opposition%20bloc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-bloc-seat-sharing-talks-in-progress-for-maharashtra-up-next-4830071%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EINDIA%20Bloc%20Seat%20Sharing%20Talks%20In%20Progress%20For%20Maharashtra%2C%20UP%20Next%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20that%20context%2C%20Mr%20Kanugolu%2C%20hailed%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bman%20of%20ideas%2C%20with%20a%20handle%20on%20the%20big%20picture%26quot%3B%2C%20would%20certainly%20be%20a%20valuable%20asset%2C%20particularly%20since%20he%20has%20worked%20with%20the%20party's%20direct%20rival%3B%20he%20was%20part%20of%20the%20BJP's%202014%20Lok%20Sabha%20campaign.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%2C%20though%2C%20is%20likely%20thinking%20(very)%20long-term.%20Wins%20in%20Karnataka%20and%20Telangana%20(and%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20another%20state%20where%20Mr%20Kanugolu%20aided%20the%20party)%20must%20be%20balanced%20against%20major%20losses%2C%20such%20as%20those%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20Chhattisgarh%20this%20year%2C%20and%20Punjab%20in%202022.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20was%20the%20ruling%20party%20in%20three%20of%20these%20four%20states%20before%20disjointed%2C%20and%20faction-ridden%2C%20campaigns%20gave%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20AAP%20(which%20picked%20up%20Punjab)%20wins%20they%20should%20not%20have%20had.%20The%20party%20now%20has%20governments%20(of%20its%20own)%20in%20just%20three%20states%20compared%20to%20the%20BJP's%2012.%20It%20is%20likely%20it%20is%20banking%20on%20Mr%20Kanugolu%2C%20and%20his%20field%20surveys%2C%20to%20win%20over%20and%20strengthen%20its%20position%20in%20key%20states%20as%20it%20looks%20to%20build%20a%20strong%20base.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaryana%2C%20where%20the%20BJP%20is%20not%20in%20a%20particularly%20strong%20position%20despite%20holding%20the%20chief%20minister's%20post%2C%20and%20Maharashtra%2C%20a%20state%20in%20turmoil%20since%20the%20acrimonious%20split%20in%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20in%20June%20last%20year%2C%20which%20dumped%20the%20Congress%20out%20of%20power%20(it%20was%20part%20of%20the%20tripartite%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20government)%2C%20seem%20good%20places%20to%20start.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAndhra%20Pradesh%2C%20which%20is%20also%20scheduled%20to%20vote%20this%20year%2C%20will%20likely%20be%20passed%20over%20by%20Mr%20Kanugolu%20given%20the%20Congress%20doesn't%20really%20have%20a%20presence%20there%2C%20despite%20the%20recent%20entrance%20of%20YS%20Sharmila.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20other%20states%20heading%20for%20Assembly%20elections%20in%202024%20are%20Odisha%2C%20where%20Chief%20Minister%20Naveen%20Patna's%20BJD%20has%20a%20stranglehold%2C%20Sikkim%2C%20and%20Arunachal%20Pradesh.%20Jharkhand%20will%20also%20vote%20but%20the%20Congress%20is%20already%20part%20of%20the%20government%20there%2C%20having%20allied%20with%20Chief%20Minister%20Hemant%20Soren's%20JMM.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20big%20test%20will%20be%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20which%2C%20if%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20order%20is%20followed%2C%20will%20hold%20a%20first%20election%20since%20the%20controversial%20scrapping%20of%20special%20status%20under%20Article%20370.%20The%20last%20Assembly%20poll%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20was%20in%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENDTV%20is%20now%20available%20on%20WhatsApp%20channels.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whatsapp.com%2Fchannel%2F0029Va4lixw7z4kcvZI9JM12%5C%22%3EClick%20on%20the%20link%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20get%20all%20the%20latest%20updates%20from%20NDTV%20on%20your%20chat.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705043520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fc0oud42_sunil-kanugolu_625x300_12_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsunil-kanugolu-2024-lok-sabha-election-sunil-kanugolu-key-to-congress-telangana-win-not-part-of-2024-planning-4847776%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sunil%20Kanugolu%20-%20the%20strategist%20credited%20with%20orchestrating%20the%20Congress'%20wins%20in%20Karnataka%20and%20Telangana%20-%20will%20not%20be%20part%20of%20its%20campaign%20for%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%22%2C%22author%22%