the%20country's%20longest%20bridge%2C%20the%20journey%20between%20the%20two%20locations%20will%20be%20shortened%20from%20the%20current%20two%20hours%20to%20around%2015-20%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fknow-all-about-indias-longest-sea-bridge-the-mumbai-trans-harbour-link-4840418%5C%22%3ERead%7C%20All%20About%20The%20Mumbai%20Trans%20Harbour%20Link%20-%20India's%20Longest%20Sea%20Bridge%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20infrastructural%20marvel%2C%20Metropolitan%20Commissioner%20of%20MMRDA%20Dr%20Sanjay%20Mukherjee%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9COn%20January%2012%2C%20PM%20Modi%20will%20inaugurate%20the%20Atal%20Setu%20-%20the%20Mumbai%20Trans%20Harbour%20Link.%20This%20is%20India's%20longest%20bridge%20built%20on%20the%20sea.%20Several%20such%20technologies%20have%20been%20used%20in%20the%20making%20of%20this%20bridge%2C%20which%20are%20used%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20India.%20The%20lights%20used%20in%20this%20bridge%20do%20not%20disturb%20the%20aquatic%20environment.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere%20is%20What's%20allowed%20and%20What's%20not%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat's%20allowed%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20maximum%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmumbai-trans-harbour-link-atal-setu-no-bikes-autos-allowed-on-indias-longest-sea-bridge-speed-limit-is-4837448%5C%22%3Espeed%20limit%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20four-wheelers%20on%20the%20Mumbai%20Trans%20Harbour%20Link%20(MTHL)%20will%20be%20100%20kmph.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20maximum%20speed%20limit%20for%20vehicles%20like%20cars%2C%20taxis%2C%20light%20motor%20vehicles%2C%20minibuses%20and%20two-axle%20buses%20is%20100%20kilometres%20per%20hour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20ascent%20and%20descent%20of%20the%20bridge%2C%20the%20speed%20will%20be%20restricted%20to%2040%20kilometres%20per%20hour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat's%20not%20allowed%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%2C%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20informed%20that%20motorbikes%2C%20auto%20rickshaws%20and%20tractors%20won't%20be%20allowed%20on%20the%20sea%20bridge%2C%20the%20police%20said%20on%20Wednesday.%20There%20will%20also%20be%20no%20entry%20for%20vehicles%20like%20motorcycles%2C%20mopeds%2C%20three-wheelers%2C%20animal-drawn%20vehicles%20and%20slow-moving%20vehicles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMulti-axle%20heavy%20vehicles%2C%20trucks%20and%20buses%20heading%20towards%20Mumbai%20won't%20have%20an%20entry%20on%20the%20Eastern%20Freeway.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmumbai-trans-harbour-link-atal-setu-no-bikes-autos-allowed-on-indias-longest-sea-bridge-speed-limit-is-4837448%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%7C%20No%20Bikes%2C%20Autos%20Allowed%20On%20India's%20Longest%20Sea%20Bridge%2C%20Speed%20Limit%20Is...%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20vehicles%20will%20have%20to%20take%20the%20Mumbai%20Port-Sewri%20Exit%20(Exit%201C)%20and%20use%20the%20MBPT%20Road%20near%20'Gadi%20Adda'%20for%20further%20movement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20official%20informed%20that%20the%20Mumbai%20police%20have%20imposed%20the%20speed%20limit%20on%20India's%20longest%20sea%20bridge%20to%20curb%20%26quot%3Bdanger%2C%20obstructions%20and%20inconvenience%20to%20the%20public.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20will%20be%20visiting%20Maharashtra%20to%20unveil%20projects%20worth%20over%20%E2%82%B9%2030%2C500%20crore%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20visit%20on%20Friday%2C%20PM%20Modi%20will%20also%20lay%20the%20foundation%20stone%20of%20an%20underground%20road%20tunnel%20connecting%20Eastern%20Freeway's%20Orange%20Gate.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmumbai-trans-harbour-link-indias-longest-sea-bridge-to-be-inaugurated-by-pm-modi-today-4845017%5C%22%3EPrime%20Minister%3C%2Fa%3E%20will%20also%20launch%20