in%20emerging%20markets%20for%20the%20day%2C%20with%202026%20notes%20jumping%203.1%20cents%20to%20about%2070%20cents%20on%20the%20dollar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan's%20performance%20under%20the%20program%20%26quot%3Bhas%20supported%20significant%20progress%20in%20stabilizing%20the%20economy%2C%26quot%3B%20Antoinette%20Sayeh%2C%20IMF%20deputy%20managing%20director%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20posted%20on%20the%20website.%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20now%20tentative%20signs%20of%20activity%20picking-up%20and%20external%20pressures%20easing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan's%20economy%20is%20expected%20to%20grow%202%25%20in%20the%20fiscal%20year%202024%20after%20contracting%20in%20the%20previous%20year%2C%20the%20IMF%20said.%20The%20nation's%20dollar%20bonds%20delivered%20returns%20of%20over%2090%25%20last%20year%20as%20default%20risks%20eased%20following%20the%20IMF%20bailout%2C%20catapulting%20them%20into%20the%20top%20rankings%20in%20emerging%20markets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EElections%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IMF%20funds%20are%20critical%20for%20Pakistan%20to%20secure%20financing%20from%20other%20creditors%20like%20Saudi%20Arabia%20and%20will%20give%20a%20boost%20to%20Pakistan's%20caretaker%20government%20under%20Prime%20Minister%20Anwaar-ul-Haq%20Kaka%20ahead%20of%20elections%20scheduled%20for%20February.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20aid%2C%20Pakistan%20remains%20under%20financial%20strain.%20The%20nine-month%20IMF%20program%20is%20set%20to%20end%20in%20March%20and%20Interim%20Finance%20Minister%20Shamshad%20Akhtar%20has%20already%20signaled%20the%20nation%20may%20need%20another%20loan%20from%20the%20IMF%20to%20support%20the%20economy.%20Pakistan%20has%20about%20%241%20billion%20in%20dollar-denominated%20debt%20due%20in%20April.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20IMF%20said%20Thursday%20that%20Pakistan%20needs%20a%20market-determined%20exchange%20rate%20to%20buffer%20external%20shocks%2C%20and%20a%20tight%20monetary%20stance%20to%20ensure%20that%20inflation%20returns%20to%20more%20moderate%20levels.%20The%20nation%20also%20needs%20to%20boost%20foreign%20reserves%2C%20the%20IMF%20said%2C%20with%20latest%20data%20showing%20reserves%20stood%20at%20%248.2%20billion%20in%20early%20January.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rupee%20has%20stabilized%20in%20recent%20months%20after%20sliding%20to%20a%20record%20low%20in%20early%20September.%20The%20currency%20traded%20at%20281%20rupees%20per%20dollar%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IMF%20has%20now%20disbursed%20a%20total%20of%20about%20%241.9%20billion%20under%20the%20program%2C%20it%20said.%20The%20approval%20came%20after%20the%20IMF%20executive%20board's%20completion%20of%20the%20first%20review%20of%20the%20%243%20billion%20Stand-By%20Arrangement%20program%20approved%20in%20July%2C%20and%20followed%20a%20staff-level%20agreement%20in%20November.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705043100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fnjt9dteo_pakistan-_625x300_12_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpakistan-secures-final-imf-approval-for-700-million-loan-ahead-of-polls-4847820%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Pakistan%20won%20final%20approval%20for%20the%20disbursement%20of%20about%20%24700%20million%20in%20aid%20from%20the%20International%20Monetary%20Fund%2C%20providing%20a%20boost%20to%20the%20embattled%20South%20Asian%20economy%20ahead%20of%20elections%20next%20month.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpakistan-secures-final-imf-approval-for-700-million-loan-ahead-of-polls-4847820%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpakistan-secures-final-imf-