5Cn%3Cp%3EMuttering%20expletives%2C%20the%20men%20hit%20the%20woman%20so%20hard%20that%20she%20falls%20to%20the%20floor.%20The%20man%20is%20also%20assaulted%20and%20then%20caught%20by%20two%20or%20three%20of%20the%20attackers%20when%20he%20tries%20to%20run%20out%20of%20the%20room.%20One%20of%20the%20attackers%20corners%20the%20woman%20near%20the%20bed%20while%20another%20hits%20her%20and%20drags%20her%20to%20the%20floor%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20out%20of%20the%20seven%20men%2C%20who%20are%20from%20the%20minority%20community%2C%20have%20been%20arrested.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705042320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fo8m276g8_karnataka-hotel-650_650x400_11_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F6-karnataka-men-who-assaulted-interfaith-couple-charged-with-rape-4846782%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20six%20men%20who%20barged%20in%20into%20the%20room%20of%20a%20Karnataka%20lodge%20and%20thrashed%20an%20interfaith%20couple%20have%20been%20charged%20with%20rape%2C%20the%20police%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F6-karnataka-men-who-assaulted-interfaith-couple-charged-with-rape-4846782%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F6-karnataka-men-who-assaulted-interfaith-couple-charged-with-rape-4846782%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F6-karnataka-men-who-assaulted-interfaith-couple-charged-with-rape-4846782%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Infy%20shares%20jump%207.6%25%20after%20Q3%20results%3B%20what%20analysts%20recommend%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705042278000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106753798%2Cimgsize-14624.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Findia-business%2Fin