%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F106753099.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EThe%20list%20continues%20with%20other%20influential%20celebrities%20such%20as%20Justin%20Bieber%2C%20Khloe%20Kardashian%2C%20Beyonce%2C%20Kim%20Kardashian%2C%20Ariana%20Grande%2C%20and%20Dwayne%20%26quot%3BThe%20Rock%26quot%3B%20Johnson.%20Finally%2C%20the%20top%20three%20positions%20are%20held%20by%20Kylie%20Jenner%2C%20Selena%20Gomez%2C%20and%20the%20top%20earner%2C%20Cristiano%20Ronaldo.%20It's%20interesting%20to%20see%20the%20earning%20potential%20of%20these%20celebrities%20through%20their%20Instagram%20presence%2C%20considering%20their%20massive%20follower%20counts%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fenglish%2Fhollywood%2Fnews%2Fselena-gomez-surpasses-kylie-jenner-as-the-highest-earning-woman-on-instagram-for-sponsored-content-while-two-prominent-men-claim-top-positions%2Farticleshow%2F106753099.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Rejecting%20Ram%20Temple%20Invite%20Might%20Hurt%20Congress%20Now%2C%20But...%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress's%20decision%20to%20give%20the%20Ram%20temple%20consecration%20a%20miss%20is%20a%20seminal%20decision%20that%20underlines%20that%20the%20party%20has%20finally%20decided%20to%20fight%20a%20long%20ideological%20battle%20versus%20the%20BJP%20and%20RSS.%20The%20Ram%20Mandir%20movement%20will%20go%20down%20in%20history%20as%20one%20that%20fundamentally%20changed%20the%20course%20of%20Indian%20politics.%20It%20was%20an%20initiative%20that%20challenged%20the%20basic%20premise%20of%20the%20freedom%20movement%2C%20which%20was%20based%20on%20a%20clear%20distinction%20between%20religion%20and%20politics.%20There%20was%20an%20understanding%20among%20freedom%20fighters%20that%20religion%20is%20a%20private%20matter%20and%20it%20should%20not%20be%20mixed%20with%20politics.%20This%20was%20the%20one%20reason%20that%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%2C%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20and%20Sardar%20Vallabhbhai%20Patel%20never%20concurred%20that%20the%20Congress%20was%20a%20Hindu%20party%20despite%20the%20repeated%20insistence%20of%20Mohammad%20Ali%20Jinnah.%20For%20Gandhi%20and%20Nehru%2C%20the%20Congress%20stood%20for%20pluralism%2C%20diversity%20and%20secularism%2C%20representing%20every%20Indian%2C%20irrespective%20of%20their%20religious%20belief.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20contrast%2C%20the%20Hindutva%20brigade%20led%20by%20Vinayak%20%26quot%3BVeer%26quot%3B%20Savarkar%20and%20the%20RSS%20espoused%20that%20India%20was%20a%20Hindu%20nation%20in%20which%20members%20of%20other%20faiths%20had%20to%20play%20second%20fiddle%2C%20and%20had%20to%20live%20at%20the%20mercy%20of%20the%20majority%20community.%20Gandhi%20was%20a%20fierce%20opponent%20of%20this%20notion%20and%20after%20his%20death%2C%20Nehru%20never%20compromised%20with%20this%20thought%20process.%20He%20was%20aware%20that%20a%20section%20of%20the%20Congress%20also%20believed%20in%20the%20ideology%20of%20Hindutva%20and%20wanted%20India%20to%20be%20called%20a%20Hindu%20Rashtra%2C%20but%20Gandhi%20and%20Nehru%20were%20such%20colossal%20figures%20that%20these%20elements%20in%20the%20Congress%20could%20never%20have%20their%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20leadership%20after%20Nehru%2C%20however%2C%20was%20neither%20so%20ideologically%20inclined%20nor%20receptive%20enough%20to%20understand%20the%20nuances%20of%20Hindutva%20politics.%20It%20is%20no%20coincidence%20that%20after%20Nehru's%20death%2C%20Hindutva%20politics%20started%20gaining%20momentum%2C%20until%20it%20reached%20where%20it%20is%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20common%20knowledge%20that%20Indira%20Gandhi%20had%20vacillated%20between%20the%20Left%20and%20the%20Right.%20If%20in%20the%201960s%20she%20was%20inspired%20by%20Left%20intellectuals%2C%20then%20after%20her%20humiliating%20defeat%20in%201977%2C%20she%20walked%20towards%20the%20Right%20and%20had%20no%20qualms%20in%20showing%20her%20%26quot%3BHindu-ness%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20public%20domain.%20This%20confusion%20became%20very%20pronounced%20during%20Rajiv%20Gandhi's%20stint.%20In%20the%201980s%2C%20after%20the%20Meenakshipuram%20mass%20conversion%20episode%2C%20when%20the%20RSS%20decided%20to%20escalate%20the%20cause%20of%20Hindutva%20and%20launched%20the%20Ram%20temple%20movement%20through%20the%20Vishwa%20Hindu%20Parishad%20(VHP)%2C%20the%20Congress%20was%20caught%20in%20a%20dilemma%20on%20whether%20to%20side%20with%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20or%20oppose%20it.%20In%20this%20confusion%2C%20the%20party%20decided%20to%20open%20the%20locks%20placed%20at%20the%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20site%20in%20Ayodhya%20and%20allowed%20a%20Shilanyas%20(foundation%20stone%20laying)%20for%20a%20Ram%20temple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20because%20of%20this%20confused%20state%20of%20affairs%20that%20then%20Prime%20Minister%20PV%20Narasimha%20Rao%20could%20not%20protect%20the%20Babri%20mosque%20at%20Ayodhya%20on%206%20December%201992.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20surprisingly%2C%20this%20was%20the%20time%20the%20Congress%20had%20started%20losing%20the%20trust%20of%20the%20people%20and%20had%20stopped%20getting%20enough%20votes%20to%20form%20a%20government%20on%20its%20own.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20BJP%20was%20gaining%20in%20strength%20with%20every%20passing%20day.%20A%20party%20that%20was%20reduced%20to%20only%20two%20MPs%20in%201984%20finally%20formed%20a%20government%20on%20its%20own%20in%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20Narendra%20Modi%20is%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20BJP.%20He%20is%20the%20most%20clearheaded%20politician%20within%20the%20RSS%20fold.%20Unlike%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20and%20LK%20Advani%2C%20he%20knows%20that%20Hindutva%20is%20the%20only%20way%20if%20the%20BJP%20has%20to%20gain%20power%20and%20continue%20to%20rule%20the%20country.%20There%20is%20no%20vacillation%20in%20his%20politics.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20Congress%2C%20after%20its%202014%20humiliation%2C%20could%20not%20decide%20what%20to%20do%20-%20should%20it%20oppose%20Hindutva%20or%20not%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%20successfully%20painted%20the%20Congress%20and%20other%20opposition%20parties%20as%20pro-Muslim%20and%20anti-Hindu.%20During%20his%20tenure%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20been%20unabashedly%20a%20pro-Hindu%20party%20that%20has%20totally%20marginalised%20Muslims%20in%20politics.%20Zero%20representation%20of%20Muslims%20in%20the%20Modi%20Cabinet%20and%20not%20even%20one%20Muslim%20BJP%20MP%20in%20parliament%20is%20testimony%20to%20that%20thought%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20section%20of%20the%20Congress%20is%20of%20the%20opinion%20that%20the%20Congress%20should%20copy%20Modi's%20template%20and%20be%20a%20Hindu%20party.%20In%20the%20recent%20elections%2C%20Kamal%20Nath%20and%20Bhupesh%20Baghel%20pursued%20that%20line%20and%20lost.%20On%20the%20contrary%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20is%20of%20the%20opinion%20that%20Hindutva%20is%20not%20the%20way%20forward%20for%20the%20Congress.%20If%20it%20has%20to%20regain%20the%20people's%20confidence%2C%20then%20it%20has%20to%20be%20seen%20to%20be%20fighting%20the%20RSS's%20Hindutva%2C%20which%2C%20according%20to%20him%2C%20is%20based%20on%20hatred%20towards%20Muslims%20and%20Christians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20Gandhi%20has%20made%20a%20slight%20modification%2C%20though.%20He%20believes%20the%20Congress%20as%20a%20political%20party%20should%20not%20be%20seen%20as%20anti-Hindu%2C%20but%20a%20clear%20distinction%20has%20to%20be%20made%20between%20Hinduism%20and%20the%20RSS's%20Hindutva.%20In%20his%20opinion%2C%20Hinduism%20is%20all%20encompassing%2C%20inclusive%20and%20does%20nothing%20to%20preach%20hatred%20towards%20anyone%2C%20whereas%20the%20RSS's%20Hindutva%20is%20exclusive%20and%20spews%20venom%20towards%20minorities%3B%20if%20Hinduism%20is%20pluralistic%20and%20embraces%20diversity%2C%20then%20RSS's%20Hindutva%20is%20hegemonic%20and%20supremacist%3B%20if%20Hinduism%20is%20a%20way%20of%20life%20then%20RSS's%20Hindutva%20is%20political.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ram%20Mandir%20campaign%20was%20a%20political%20movement.%20The%20idea%20was%20to%20undermine%20and%20discredit%20the%20idea%20of%20secularism%20and%20to%20win%20the%20trust%20of%20Hindus%20to%20form%20a%20government%20at%20the%20Centre%20and%20create%2C%20in%20the%20grand%20scheme%2C%20a%20Hindu%20Rashtra.%20The%20demolition%20of%20Babri%20Masjid%20was%20a%20declaration%20that%20Muslims%20can%20no%20longer%20claim%20to%20be%20equal%20and%20India%20would%20be%20run%20by%20Hindus%20only.%20This%20is%20antithetical%20to%20the%20basic%20idea%20of%20India%20that%20was%20so%20dear%20to%20Gandhi%2C%20Nehru%2C%20Patel%2C%20Subhash%20Chandra%20Bose%20and%20BR%20Ambedkar.%20In%20this%20stream%20of%20thought%2C%20there%20cannot%20be%20any%20opposition%20to%20the%20Ram%20Temple%3B%20there%20can%20be%20no%20Hinduism%20without%20Ram.%20Ram%20is%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20India's%20imagination%2C%20its%20basic%20ethos%20of%20Hindu%20memory.%20Gandhi%20had%20proudly%20called%20himself%20Hindu.%20However%2C%20his%20Ram%20is%20not%20what%20the%20RSS%20believes.%20Gandhi%20wrote%20in%201946%20in%20Harijan%20magazine.%20%26quot%3BMy%20Ram%2C%20the%20Ram%20of%20our%20prayer%20is%20not%20the%20historical%20Ram%2C%20the%20son%20of%20Dasaratha%2C%20the%20king%20of%20Ayodhya.%20He%20is%20the%20eternal%2C%20the%20unborn%2C%20the%20one%20without%20a%20second.%26quot%3B%20In%201929%2C%20he%20explained%20in%20Young%20India%20what%20he%20meant%20by%20Ram%20Rajya.%20%26quot%3BBy%20Ram%20Rajya%20I%20don't%20mean%20a%20Hindu%20State%2C%20what%20I%20meant%20is%20rule%20of%20God%2C%20the%20state%20ruled%20by%20divine%20...%20a%20true%20Ram%20Rajya%20would%20ensure%20equal%20rights%20to%20both%20Prince%20and%20pauper.%26quot%3B%20For%20him%2C%20'Ram%20Rajya%20is%20an%20ideal%20state'%20in%20which%20there%20is%20no%20discrimination%20of%20any%20kind%20based%20on%20faith%2C%20caste%2C%20class%20and%20gender.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20to%20define%20Hinduism%2C%20Nehru%20quoted%20Gandhi.%20%26quot%3BIf%20I%20were%20asked%20to%20define%20the%20Hindu%20creed%2C%20I%20should%20simply%20say%3A%20Search%20after%20truth%20through%20non-violent%20means.%20A%20man%20may%20not%20believe%20in%20God%20and%20still%20call%20himself%20a%20Hindu...Hinduism%20is%20the%20religion%20of%20truth.%20Truth%20is%20god.%26quot%3B%20Gandhi%20and%20Nehru%20were%20among%20the%20greatest%20of%20statesmen%20the%20world%20has%20seen.%20Their%20idea%20of%20religion%20and%20state%20can%20never%20be%20narrow.%20Hinduism%20for%20them%20was%20spiritual%2C%20an%20inward%20journey%2C%20not%20ritualistic.%20Certainly%20not%20political.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%2FRSS%20call%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20a%20matter%20of%20faith%2C%20and%20those%20who%20don't%20visit%20it%20will%20be%20called%20anti-Hindu%20or%20anti-Ram.%20It%20is%20this%20narrow%20construct%20of%20Hinduism%20and%20of%20Ram%20that%20should%20be%20contested.%20The%20Congress%2C%20by%20declining%20the%20invitation%20to%20visit%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20on%20January%2022%2C%20has%20decided%20to%20fight%20for%20the%20original%20Idea%20of%20India.%20This%20path%20can%20be%20challenging%2C%20difficult%20and%20long.%20It%20might%20hurt%20the%20party%20in%20the%20short%20term%20(which%20I%20don't%20believe)%2C%20but%20it%20will%20definitely%20reap%20dividends%20in%20the%20end%2C%20if%20the%20party%20has%20to%20regain%20the%20confidence%20of%20the%20people.%20The%20problem%20with%20the%20Congress%20was%20not%20Ram%20Mandir%20but%20the%20confusion%20about%20its%20moorings.%20Let's%20hope%20it%20has%20rediscovered%20its%20real%20self%20and%20remains%20steadfast%20on%20that%20path%20now%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Ashutosh%20is%20author%20of%20'Hindu%20Rashtra'%20and%20Editor%2C%20satyahindi.com.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%