0the%20Ram%20temple%20consecration%20ceremony%20on%20January%2022.%20In%20a%20special%20message%20to%20the%20nation%2C%20he%20said%20he%20felt%20emotional%20and%20overwhelmed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20emotional.%20For%20the%20first%20time%20in%20my%20life%2C%20I%20am%20experiencing%20such%20feelings%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%2010-minute%20audio%20message%20posted%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20said%20it%20was%20his%20good%20fortune%20to%20be%20able%20to%20witness%20the%20%26quot%3BPran%20Pratishtha%26quot%3B%20ceremony%2C%20in%20which%20an%20idol%20of%20Ram%20Lalla%2C%20or%20infant%20Ram%2C%20will%20be%20placed%20at%20the%20new%20Ram%20Temple%20in%20Ayodhya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGod%2C%20he%20said%2C%20had%20chosen%20him%20as%20an%20instrument%20to%20represent%20all%20Indians%20at%20what%20he%20described%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bhistoric%20and%20sacred%20moment%26quot%3B.%20To%20prepare%20for%20it%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said%20he%20would%20follow%20strict%20rules%20prescribed%20in%20scriptures%20and%20as%20guided%20by%20saints.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20our%20scriptures%20say%2C%20for%20the%20yajna%20(sacrifice)%20of%20God%2C%20for%20worship%2C%20we%20must%20awaken%20the%20divine%20consciousness%20within%20ourselves.%20For%20this%2C%20the%20scriptures%20prescribe%20vows%20and%20strict%20rules%20that%20need%20to%20be%20followed%20before%20the%20consecration.%20Therefore%2C%20following%20the%20guidance%20I%20have%20received%20from%20saints%20on%20this%20spiritual%20journey...%20They%20have%20suggested%20the%20principles%20of%20conduct%20(yam-niyam)%2C%20and%20I%20am%20starting%20a%20special%20observance%20of%2011%20days%20from%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20referred%20to%20Swami%20Vivekananda's%20birth%20anniversary%20today%2C%20calling%20it%20a%20%26quot%3Bjoyous%20coincidence%26quot%3B.%20He%20also%20cited%20the%20birth%20anniversary%20of%20Jijabai%2C%20the%20mother%20of%20Chhatrapati%20Shivaji%2C%20recalling%20his%20own%20mother%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20urged%20Indians%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20him%20through%20his%20Namo%20app%20and%20sought%20their%20blessings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20though%20I%20want%20to%2C%20I%20cannot%20capture%20the%20depth%2C%20vastness%2C%20and%20intensity%20of%20it%20in%20words.%20You%20can%20understand%20my%20state.%20The%20dream%20that%20many%20generations%20have%20cherished%20for%20years%2C%20I%20am%20fortunate%20to%20be%20present%20at%20its%20fulfilment.%20The%20Lord%20has%20made%20me%20a%20representative%20of%20all%20Indians.%20I%20am%20just%20an%20instrument.%20This%20is%20a%20huge%20responsibility%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20Prime%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20seek%20blessing%20from%20people.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister's%20message%20comes%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20intense%20politics%20over%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20event%2C%20with%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20slamming%20opposition%20parties%20like%20the%20Congress%20for%20skipping%20the%20January%2022%20ceremony.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20leaders%20Sonia%20Gandhi%2C%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20and%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%20have%20declined%20the%20invite%2C%20calling%20the%20event%20a%20%26quot%3Bpolitical%20project%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20BJP%20and%20its%20ideological%20mentor%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%20and%20asserting%20that%20%26quot%3Breligion%20is%20a%20personal%20matter%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Left%20and%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20have%20also%20declared%20they%20will%20forgo%20the%20ceremony.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20put%20out%20a%20%26quot%3Bname%20and%20shame%26quot%3B%20tweet%20blasting%20some%20of%20the%20opposition%20leaders%20with%20the%20caption%3A%20%26quot%3BNote%20the%20faces%20of%20Sanatan%20opponents%20who%20rejected%20the%20invite%20for%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20ceremony%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20no