.com%2Fmark-zuckerberg-wasnt-sure-which-ai-breakthrough-google-ceo-praised-2024-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705037705000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a0b56843bb77284b9c8518%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-zuckerberg-wasnt-sure-which-ai-breakthrough-google-ceo-praised-2024-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Speaking%20to%20Zuckerberg%20at%20a%20conference%20in%20Idaho%20in%202021%2C%20Pichai%20expressed%20admiration%20for%20a%20Facebook%20breakthrough%20in%20AI%2C%20per%20Bloomberg.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ktan%40businessinsider.com%20(Kwan%20Wei%20Kevin%20Tan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-zuckerberg-wasnt-sure-which-ai-breakthrough-google-ceo-praised-2024-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BMadam%20Was%20Calm%26quot%3B%3A%20Cab%20Driver%20Who%20Helped%20Cops%20Catch%20Murder%20Accused%20CEO%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESuchana%20Seth%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20an%20AI%20start-up%20arrested%20for%20allegedly%20killing%20her%20four-year-old%20son%2C%20was%20quiet%20throughout%20her%20journey%20from%20Goa%20to%20Karnataka%20in%20a%20taxi%2C%20said%20the%20driver%20of%20the%20vehicle%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20to%20reporters%20at%20Candolim%20in%20North%20Goa%20on%20Thursday%2C%20Ray%20John%2C%20the%20taxi%20driver%20who%20helped%20the%20police%20arrest%20Seth%2C%20said%20she%20was%20calm%20and%20did%20not%20utter%20a%20single%20word%20during%20the%20entire%20trip%20that%20lasted%20more%20than%2010%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeth%20(39)%20was%20arrested%20from%20Chitradurga%20in%20Karnataka%20on%20Monday%20night%20while%20she%20was%20travelling%20in%20the%20taxi%20with%20her%20son's%20body%20stuffed%20in%20a%20bag%20and%20brought%20to%20Goa%20on%20Tuesday.%20A%20court%20in%20Mapusa%20town%20remanded%20her%20in%20police%20custody%20for%20six%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20is%20accused%20of%20killing%20the%20child%20in%20a%20Candolim-based%20service%20apartment%20in%20Goa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20John%20said%20the%20service%20apartment%20staff%20booked%20his%20taxi%20for%20Seth.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20reached%20the%20service%20apartment%2C%20she%20(Seth)%20asked%20me%20to%20carry%20her%20bag%20from%20the%20reception%20to%20the%20taxi.%20It%20was%20heavy%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20taxi%20driver%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20asked%20her%20whether%20we%20could%20remove%20some%20belongings%20from%20the%20bag%20to%20make%20it%20lighter.%20But%20she%20refused.%20We%20had%20to%20drag%20the%20bag%20to%20the%20boot%20of%20the%20car%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20driver%20said%20that%20the%20only%20time%20she%20spoke%20was%20when%20she%20asked%20him%20to%20get%20a%20bottle%20of%20water%20when%20they%20reached%20Bicholim%20town%20in%20North%20Goa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20John%20said%20when%20they%20were%20heading%20to%20Bengaluru%20on%20Monday%2C%20there%20was%20a%20huge%20traffic%20jam%20at%20Chorla%20ghat%20section%20on%20the%20Karnataka-Goa%20border.%20The%20police%20told%20him%20that%20it%20would%20take%20at%20least%20four%20hours%20to%20get%20the%20traffic%20cleared.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20exaggerated%20the%20time%20and%20told%20madam%20(Seth)%20that%20it%20would%20take%20six%20hours%20to%20clear%20the%20road%20and%20suggested%20that%20we%20could%20turn%20back%20and%20head%20to%20the%20airport.%20But%20she%20insisted%20on%20continuing%20by%20road%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20driver%2C%20stressing%20that%20he%20felt%20something%20was%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20taxi%20driver%20said%20he%20later%20received%20a%20call%20from%20the%20Goa%20police%2C%20alerting%20him%20that%20there%20was%20something%20suspicious%20about%20his%20passenger.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Calangute%20police%20told%20me%20to%20search%20for%20a%20nearby%20police%20station%20and%20take%20her%20there.%20I%20tried%20searching%20on%20Google%20Maps%20and%20GPS%20but%20didn't%20find%20any.%20I%20even%20looked%20for%20cops%20at%20toll%20plazas%20but%20there%20were%20none%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlarmed%20by%20the%20call%20from%20the%20police%2C%20the%20taxi%20driver%20said%20he%20bought%20some%20more%20time%20under%20the%20pretext%20of%20stopping%20by%20a%20roadside%20restaurant.%20There%20he%20learnt%20that%20a%20police%20station%20was%20just%20500%20metres%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20one%20and%20a%20half%20hours%20away%20from%20Bengaluru.%20I%20drove%20to%20the%20Aiyamangala%20police%20station%20(in%20Chitradurga%20district%20of%20Karnataka)%2C%20while%20a%20Calangute%20police%20official%20remained%20on%20line%20with%20me%20on%20the%20phone%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20John%20said%20it%20took%20almost%2015%20minutes%20before%20the%20inspector%20concerned%20came%20out.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20madam%20was%20calm%20and%20was%20sitting%20in%20the%20car%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20searched%20her%20bag%20and%20found%20the%20child's%20body%20in%20it%2C%20said%20John.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20police%20asked%20her%20whether%20it%20was%20her%20son.%20She%20calmly%20said%20%E2%80%98yes'%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20accused%20has%20told%20the%20police%20that%20she%20and%20her%20husband%20were%20estranged%20and%20their%20divorce%20proceedings%20were%20currently%20underway%2C%20according%20to%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Seth's%20LinkedIn%20page%2C%20she%20is%20the%20Chief%20Executive%20Officer%20(CEO)%20of%20start-up%20Mindful%20AI%20Lab%20and%20was%20among%20the%20top%20'100%20Brilliant%20Women%20in%20AI%20Ethics%20for%202021'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20had%20checked%20into%20the%20service%20apartment%20in%20North%20Goa%20on%20January%206%20along%20with%20her%20son.%20After%20staying%20there%20for%20two%20days%2C%20she%20info