0After%20Red%20Sea%20Attacks%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F12105903%2FHouthis.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20States%20and%20Britain%20on%20Friday%20began%20carrying%20out%20strikes%20against%20sites%20used%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fhouthis%2Ft-67629191%5C%22%3EHouthi%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0rebel%20group%20in%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fyemen%2Ft-38381376%5C%22%3EYemen%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUS%20officials%20said%20targets%20included%20logistical%20hubs%2C%20air%20defence%20systems%2C%20and%20weapons%20storage%20locations.%20US%20media%20reported%20that%20the%20strikes%20involved%20fighter%20jets%20and%20Tomahawk%20missiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Houthis%20are%20backed%20by%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Firan%2Ft-18996175%5C%22%3EIran%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20control%20large%20swathes%20of%20western%20Yemen%2C%20including%20the%20capital%2C%20Sanaa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBiden%20hails%20%E2%80%98united%E2%80%99%20response%20to%20%E2%80%98reckless%E2%80%99%20Houthi%20attacks%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUS%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20said%20the%20strikes%20represented%20a%20%E2%80%9Cunited%20and%20resolute%E2%80%9D%20response%20to%20Houthi%20attacks%20on%20international%20ships%20and%20that%20the%20US%C2%A0would%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20hesitate%20to%20direct%20further%20measures%E2%80%9D%20against%20the%20militant%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20response%20of%20the%20international%20community%20to%20these%20reckless%20attacks%20has%20been%20united%20and%20resolute%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20released%20by%20the%20White%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%20said%20the%20US%20and%20UK%20strikes%20were%20carried%20out%20with%20support%20from%20Australia%2C%20Bahrain%2C%20Canada%2C%20and%20the%20Netherlands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20targeted%20strike