0almost%20all%20boxes.%20India%20romped%20home%20to%20a%20six-wicket%20win%20with%20players%20like%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Shivam%20Dube%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F107521-shivam-dubey-playerprofile%5C%22%3EShivam%20Dube%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Axar%20Patel%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F63024-akshar-rajeshbhai-patel-playerprofile%5C%22%3EAxar%20Patel%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20others%20giving%20a%20good%20account%20of%20themselves.%20However%2C%20one%20box%20that%20was%20left%20unchecked%20was%20a%20solid%20batting%20show%20by%20Rohit%20Sharma.%20Playing%20his%20first%20T20I%20in%2014%20months%2C%20Rohit%20Sharma%20got%20out%20on%200%20after%20a%20horrific%20mix-up%20with%20fellow%20opener%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Shubman%20Gill%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F108578-shubman-gill-playerprofile%5C%22%3EShubman%20Gill%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20happened%20on%20the%20second%20ball%20of%20the%20first%20over%20of%20the%20Indian%20innings.%20Rohit%20Sharma%20called%20for%20a%20run%20but%20Shubman%20Gill%20kept%20looking%20at%20the%20ball.%20Rohit%20Sharma%2C%20by%20then%20had%20already%20ran%20towards%20the%20other%20ends.%20Afghanistan%20players%20were%20alert%20enough%20to%20run%20out%20the%20India%20captain.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLook%20at%20him%20(Shubman)%2C%20he%20is%20watching%20and%20watching.%20Rohit%20had%20called%20yes%20(for%20a%20run).%20Won't%20repeat%20what%20he%20said%20because%20it%20is%20not%20very%20nice.%20But%20Rohit%20Sharma%20is%20absolutely%20spot%20on%2C%20he%20is%20in%20the%20right%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20of%20the%20commentators.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20two%20things%20in%20running%20between%20the%20wickets%20first%20is%20cross%2C%20and%20second%20the%20gauging%20the%20pace%20at%20which%20your%20partner%20can%20run.%20It%20is%20not%20about%20you%20being%20quick