F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F13EE6%2Fproduction%2F_132283618_nhaley2-index-epa.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-67948573%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22She's%20betting%20the%20ex-president%20is%20more%20vulnerable%20than%20polls%20suggest.%20It%E2%80%99s%20still%20a%20very%20long%20shot.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A23%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-67948573%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-67948573.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-67948573.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Electoral%20Manipulation%20and%20Ennui%20Permeate%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20Poll%20Process%26nbsp%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F12092542%2FUntitled-design-12.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20lower%20house%20of%20parliament%20was%20dissolved%20in%20August%2C%20a%20caretaker%20government%20under%20Prime%20Minister%20Anwaar%20ul-Haq%20Kakar%20was%20set%20up%20to%20oversee%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20general%20elections%20scheduled%20for%20November%202023.%20But%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20Pakistan%20(ECP)%20said%20it%20needed%20more%20time%20to%20redraw%20constituencies%20based%20on%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20population%20census%2C%20and%20national%20elections%20were%20deferred%20till%20February%208%2C%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20the%20upper%20house%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20parliament%20has%20passed%20a%20non-binding%20resolution%20demanding%20a%20further%20delay%20in%20the%20general%20elections.%20With%20the%20constitutional%20timeframe%20for%20holding%20elections%20having%20passed%2C%20people%20are%20asking%20whether%20they%20will%20be%20held%20at%20all.%20Indeed%20in%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20case%2C%20predicting%20anything%20beyond%20a%20few%20months%20is%20hazardous.%20What%20remains%20certain%20is%20uncertainty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20resolution%20seeking%20a%20delay%20in%20the%20elections%2C%20tabled%20by%20independent%20Senator%20Dilawar%20Khan%20on%20January%205%20with%20only%2015%20lawmakers%20in%20attendance%20cited%20the%20cold%20weather%20in%20Balochistan%20and%20Khyber%20Pakhtunkhwa%2C%20serious%20threats%20to%20the%20lives%20of%20politicians%20like%20JUI-F%20chief%20Fazlur%20Rehman%2C%20the%20spike%20in%20attacks%20on%20security%20forces%20and%20citizens%2C%20and%20the%20resurgence%20of%20COVID-19.%20The%20Senate%20Secretariat%20later%20issued%20a%20notification%20regarding%20the%20resolution%E2%80%99s%20approval%20which%20was%20roundly%20rejected%20by%20all%20leading%20political%20parties.%20Although%20the%20house%20failed%20to%20meet%20the%20quorum%20requirements%20for%20such%20a%20move%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20was%20subsequently%20approached%20to%20declare%20the%20resolution%20illegal%20and%20act%20against%20its%20backers.%20Pakistan%20People%E2%80%99s%20Party%20(PPP)%20Senator%20Sherry%20Rehman%20declared%20that%20the%20party%20wanted%20timely%20elections%3B%20%E2%80%98standing%20firmly%20against%E2%80%99%2C%20the%20Pakistan%20Muslim%20League-Nawaz%20(PML-N)%20labelled%20it%20a%20backdoor%20conspiracy%20to%20postpone%20elections%3B%C2%A0%20and%20Jamaat-i-Islami%20(JI)%20Senator%20Mushtaq%20Ahmed%20submitted%20a%20fresh%20resolution%20in%20the%20upper%20house%2C%20emphasising%20the%20need%20to%20ensure%20the%20timely%20conduct%20of%20the%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERuling%20out%20any%20possibility%20of%20boycotting%20the%20polls%2C%20Pakistan%20Tehreek-e-Insaf%20(PTI)%20Chairman%20Barrister%20Gohar%20Khan%2C%20told%20reporters%20that%20the%20party%20wanted%20elections%20on%20the%20given%20date%20of%20February%208.%20Prior%20to%20this%20in%20an%20opinion%20piece%20carried%20in%C2%A0%3Cem%3EThe%20Economis%3C%2Fem%3Et%20by%20Imran%20Khan%20from%20Adiala%20Jail%20in%20Rawalpindi%2C%20the%2071%20year%20old%20deposed%20premier%20expressed%20fears%20that%20the%20scheduled%20elections%20might%20not%20take%20place%20at%20all%2C%20alluding%20to%20his%20%E2%80%98engineered%E2%80%99%20removal%20from%20power%20in%202022%20by%20the%20establishment%20%E2%80%98under%20pressure%20from%20America%E2%80%99%20and%20the%20lack%20of%20%E2%80%98level%20playing%20field%E2%80%99%20in%20the%20elections.%20The%20article%E2%80%99s%20most%20exigent%20claim%20however%20is%20that%20Nawaz%20Sharif%20%E2%80%9Chas%20struck%20a%20deal%20with%20the%20establishment%20whereby%20it%20will%20support%20his%20acquittal%20and%20throw%20its%20weight%20behind%20him%20in%20the%20upcoming%20elections%E2%80%9D.%20Whether%20or%20not%20the%20article%20was%20ghosted%2C%20given%20that%20Imran%20Khan%20is%20in%20sequestered%20incarceration%20and%20not%20even%20allowed%20to%20appear%20in%20court%2C%20the%20fact%20that%20his%20message%20was%20relayed%20has%20piqued%20the%20establishment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEchoing%20a%20similar%20thought%2C%C2%A0%3Cem%3EDawn%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0journalist%20Zahid%20Hussain%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2Fec186a79-c7d9-4177-af5f-533ed853a9aa%3Fj%3DeyJ1IjoiYWt5Mm8ifQ.6MWfvlP9rau_ovHEjX2OsfccTssIZEXNjPP_vKEvs5I%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2Fec186a79-c7d9-4177-af5f-533ed853a9aa%3Fj%253DeyJ1IjoiYWt5Mm8ifQ.6MWfvlP9rau_ovHEjX2OsfccTssIZEXNjPP_vKEvs5I%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1705111744671000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw1YZtD7Yx9cV_sOO9OwaEwL%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eequates%20the%20upcoming%20election%20to%20yet%20another%20%E2%80%98process%20of%20selection%2C%E2%80%99%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20which%20the%20most%20brazen%20pre-poll%20manipulation%20is%20underway%2C%20making%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20legitimacy%20of%20the%20democratic%20transition%20extremely%20doubtful.%20What%20is%20happening%20now%20has%20perhaps%20not%20been%20witnessed%20even%20under%20military%20rule.%20The%20dismantling%20of%20the%20failed%20project%20has%20been%20turned%20into%20an%20exercise%20in%20vengeance.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20uncertainty%20marking%20the%20political%20atmosphere%2C%20electioneering%20is%20yet%20to%20hit%20full%20throttle.%20Party%20leaders%20aren%E2%80%99t%20holding%20the%20kind%20of%20rallies%20or%20making%20the%20kind%20of%20appearances%20typical%20of%20pre-election%20campaigning.%20In%20the%20run%20up%20to%20the%202018%20elections%2C%20it%20was%20the%20PML-N%20that%20was%20being%20hounded%20by%20the%20military%20establishment.%20This%20time%20around%2C%20the%20party%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20appear%20to%20have%20moved%20beyond%20the%20board%20meeting%20phase%20and%20its%20election%20manifesto%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20released.%20In%20a%20role-swap%20with%20Imran%20Khan%2C%20a%20redeemed%20Nawaz%20Sharif%20is%20the%20apparent%20favourite%20of%20the%20army%2C%20which%20is%20probably%20why%20the%20PML-N%20has%20yet%20to%20start%20campaigning%20in%20earnest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmidst%20speculation%20over%20differences%20with%20his%20father%20Asif%20Ali%20Zardari%2C%20PPP%20Chairman%20Bilawal%20Bhutto-Zardari%20has%20been%20appealing%20to%20make%20%E2%80%9Cold%20politicians%20sit%20at%20home%2C%E2%80%9D%20and%20select%20him%2C%20expressing%20that%20he%20wishes%20to%20%E2%80%9Cbecome%20the%C2%A0%3Cem%3Elaadla%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0(favourite)%20of%20the%20public.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PTI%20has%20fallen%20out%20of%20favour%20with%20the%20%E2%80%98establishment%E2%80%99%C2%A0%20because%20of%20its%20involvement%20in%20the%20May%209%20unrest.%20Military%20courts%20are%20set%20to%20prosecute%20PTI%20supporters%20who%20were%20involved%20in%20riots%20and%20violence.%20While%20the%20PTI%20has%20fielded%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20candidates%20for%20the%20upcoming%20general%20elections%2C%20almost%2090%20percent%20of%20nominations%20from%20important%20leaders%20failed%20to%20stand%20the%20ECP%20scrutiny%20exercise%20that%20ended%20on%20December%2030.%20The%20nomination%20papers%20of%20several%20of%20its%20election%20candidates%20were%20rejected%2C%20including%20that%20of%20Imran%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98No.%202%E2%80%99%2C%20Shah%20Mehmood%20Qureshi%2C%20from%20three%20constituencies%20of%20Multan%2C%20south%20Punjab.%20After%20annulling%20the%20PTI%E2%80%99s%20intra-party%20election%2C%20the%20ECP%20also%20stripped%20the%20party%20of%20its%20electoral%20%E2%80%98bat%E2%80%99%20symbol.%20The%20PTI%E2%80%99s%20hyped%20virtual%20manifesto%20launch%20on%20January%207%20was%20trammeled%20by%20a%20blackout%20of%20social%20media%20sites%20reported%20throughout%20Pakistan.%20Nevertheless%2C%20reminiscent%20of%20its%20sweep%20through%20Khyber%20Pakhtunkhwa%20in%20the%202018%20elections%2C%20its%20popularity%20appears%20to%20intact.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ECP%E2%80%99s%20credibility%20took%20a%20hit%20when%20it%20failed%20to%20hold%20elections%20in%20May%202023%20in%20Punjab%20and%20K-P%2C%20and%20later%20in%20November%202023%2C%20and%20its%20current%20discriminatory%20attitude%20towards%20the%20PTI%20prevents%20a%20genuine%20code%20of%20conduct%20from%20manifesting%20itself.%20But%20all%20political%20parties%20in%20Pakistan%20have%20had%20to%20face%20this%20at%20some%20point.%20The%20political%20uncertainty%20weighs%20on%20the%20economy.%20Foreign%20firms%20are%20reported%20to%20have%20divested%20their%20assets%20or%20temporarily%20reduced%20or%20halted%20their%20operations%20in%20Pakistan%20since%202022.%20State-owned%20commercial%20entities%20incurred%20staggering%20losses%20amounting%20to%20PKR%201.4%20trillion%20in%202021%20and%20%E2%80%9822.%20Proposed%20strategies%20all%20seem%20to%20be%20looking%20for%20injection%20foreign%20funds%20as%20a%20panacea%20for%20the%20economic%20malaise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20matter%20which%20political%20party%E2%80%99s%20rise%20to%20power%20is%20manipulated%2C%20a%20certain%20ennui%20in%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20political%20process%20can%20be%20detected.%20Being%20championed%20by%20the%20%E2%80%98establishment%E2%80%99%20brings%20its%20own%20set%20of%20challenges%2C%20primarily%20the%20problem%20of%20legitimacy%2C%20leaving%20political%20parties%20struggling%20to%20articulate%20their%20own%20strategy.%20Meanwhile%20tough%20decisions%20for%20restructuring%20the%20economy%20and%20governance%20elude%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3EVaishali%3C%2Fspan%3E%C2%A0Basu%20Sharma%20is%20a%20strategic%20and%20economic%20affairs%20analyst.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20piece%20was%20first%20published%20on%20The%20India%20Cable%20%E2%80%93%20a%20premium%20newsletter%20from%20The%20Wire%20%26amp%3B%20Galileo%20Ideas%20%E2%80%93%20and%20has%20been%20updated%20and%20republished%20here.%20To%20subscribe%20to%20The%20India%20Cable%2C%20click%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Ftheindiacable.com%2F%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705031854000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F12092542%2FUntitled-design-12.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Felectoral-manipulation-and-ennui-permeate-pakistans-poll-process%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Being%20championed%20by%20the%20%E2%80%98establishment%E2%80%99%20brings%20its%20own%20set%20of%20challenges%2C%20primarily%20the%20problem%20of%20legitimacy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Felectoral-manipulation-and-ennui-permeate-pakistans-poll-process%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UK's%20PM%20Rishi%20Sunak%20says%20strikes%20against%20Huthis%20'necessary%20and%20proportionate'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705031773000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106747337%2Cimgsize-25460.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiat