%20Houthi%20targets%20in%20Yemen%20over%20recent%20attacks%20on%20Red%20Sea%20shipping%20were%20%26quot%3Bnecessary%20and%20proportionate%26quot%3B%2C%20UK%20Prime%20Minister%20Rishi%20Sunak%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDespite%20the%20repeated%20warnings%20from%20the%20international%20community%2C%20the%20Houthis%20have%20continued%20to%20carry%20out%20attacks%20in%20the%20Red%20Sea%2C%26quot%3B%20Sunak%20said%20in%20a%20statement%2C%20using%20an%20alternative%20spelling%20for%20the%20Houthis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20therefore%20taken%20limited%2C%20necessary%20and%20proportionate%20action%20in%20self-defence%2C%20alongside%20the%20United%20States...%20to%20degrade%20Houthi%20military%20capabilities%20and%20protect%20global%20shipping%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESunak's%20statement%20followed%20comments%20by%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20about%20the%20strikes%20carried%20out%20against%20the%20Houthis%2C%20who%20control%20wide%20areas%20of%20Yemen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Houthis%20have%20stepped%20up%20attacks%20in%20recent%20weeks%20on%20shipping%20in%20the%20Red%20Sea%2C%20a%20vital%20waterway%20through%20which%2012%20percent%20of%20world%20trade%20flows.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHouthi%20television%20channel%20Al-Massirah%20said%20the%20air%20strikes%20hit%20the%20capital%20Sanaa%20as%20well%20as%20the%20cities%20of%20Hodeida%20and%20Saada.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUS%20and%20British%20forces%20this%20week%20shot%20down%2018%20drones%20and%20three%20missiles%20fired%20by%20Houthi%20rebels%20in%20the%20Red%20Sea%20in%20what%20Washington%20called%20a%20%26quot%3Bcomplex%20Iranian-designed%26quot%3B%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUK%20Defence%20Secretary%20Grant%20Shapps%20said%20on%20Twitter%20that%20four%20Royal%20Air%20Force%20Typhoon%20fighter%20jets%20had%20taken%20part%20in%20Friday's%20strikes%20against%20Houthi%20targets%20alongside%20US%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESunak%20described%20the%20Houthi's%20actions%20as%20