iness%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20and%20UK%20launched%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-launches-strikes-houthis-following-shipping-attacks-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eretaliatory%20strikes%20against%20Houthi%20rebels%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0in%20Yemen%20on%20Thursday%2C%20targeting%20radar%20stations%2C%C2%A0weapons%C2%A0storage%20facilities%2C%20and%20launch%20sites%20linked%20to%20the%C2%A0militants%2C%20a%20US%20defense%20official%20confirmed%20to%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20large-scale%20strikes%20come%20after%20the%20Iran-backed%20rebel%20group%20conducted%20dozens%C2%A0of%C2%A0attacks%20against%C2%A0commercial%C2%A0ships%C2%A0sailing%20through%20the%20Red%20Sea%20and%20other%20key%C2%A0trade%C2%A0routes%20since%20November.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Houthis%20have%20claimed%20that%20the%20assaults%20are%20in%20response%20to%20Israel's%20attacks%20on%20Hamas%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%C2%A0although%20US%20officials%20have%20pushed%20back%20on%20this%2C%20and%20slammed%20the%20militants%20for%20creating%20a%20global%20problem%20by%20attacking%20international%20shipping%20lanes%20in%20key%20waterways.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20UK%20defense%20ministry%20said%20in%20planning%20the%20strikes%2C%20%26quot%3Bparticular%20care%20was%20taken%20to%20minimize%20any%20risks%20to%20civilians%2C%20and%20any%20such%20risks%20were%20mitigated%20further%20by%20the%20decision%20to%20conduct%20the%20strikes%20during%20the%20night.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20detailed%20results%20of%20the%20strikes%20are%20being%20assessed%2C%20but%20early%20indications%20are%20that%20the%20Houthis'%20ability%20to%20threaten%20merchant%20shipping%20has%20taken%20a%20blow%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20ministry%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Mick%20Ryan%2C%20a%20retired%20Major%20General%20in%20the%20Australian%20Army%20and%20a%20military%20strategist%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20effectively%20suppressing%20the%20rebel%20group's%20mis