20to%20Hyderabad%20and%20began%20operating%20in%20Telangana%20in%20an%20independent%20capacity.%20There%20was%20talk%20that%20she%20would%20join%20the%20Congress%20party%20in%20Telangana%20but%20with%20local%20Congress%20workers%20not%20very%20enthusiastic%2C%20Sharmila%20has%20now%20been%20moved%20over%20to%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20which%20will%20go%20to%20polls%20early%20next%20year.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20creation%20of%20Telangana%20that%20happened%20nearly%20ten%20years%20ago%20though%20not%20forgotten%20by%20folks%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20today%20has%20little%20impact.%20This%20would%20mean%20that%20that%20animosity%20against%20the%20Congress%20party%20is%20all%20but%20gone%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%9CThe%20party%20now%20requires%20a%20new%20leader%20to%20take%20it%20forward.%20Whether%20Sharmila%20can%20galvanise%20the%20outfit%20is%20something%20that%20has%20to%20be%20watched%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20a%20senior%20Congress%20leader%20who%20hopes%20that%20the%20new%20leader%20would%20be%20successful.%20The%20leader%20feels%20that%20since%20the%20party%20has%20been%20more%20or%20less%20reduced%20to%20zero%20it%20will%20be%20easier%20for%20Sharmila%20to%20make%20a%20mark.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Being%20Jagan%E2%80%99s%20sister%2C%20she%20is%20uniquely%20placed%20to%20encroach%20on%20some%20of%20his%20support%20base%2C%20Congress%20workers%20say.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESharmila%20gave%20indications%20of%20her%20plans%20by%20talking%20of%20minorities%20and%20the%20situation%20in%20Manipur.%20This%20is%20seen%20as%20a%20direct%20attack%20on%20her%20brother%2C%20Jagan.%20Both%20Jagan%20(and%20Sharmila)%20are%20Christians%20and%20there%20is%20an%20undercurrent%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20that%20Christians%20are%20not%20getting%20the%20right%20treatment%20in%20the%20state%20in%20spite%20of%20Jagan.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fandhra-pradesh-in-flux-political-pesarattu-in-the-making%5C%22%3EAndhra%20Pradesh%20Is%20a%20Political%20Pesarattu%20in%20the%20Making%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20disputed%20by%20Jagan%20acolytes.%20In%20Manipur%20too%2C%20Christians%20have%20been%20among%20people%20who%20are%20at%20the%20receiving%20end%20of%20the%20recent%20violence.%20Jagan%20is%20seen%20to%20be%20on%20the%20side%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20which%20is%20perceived%20as%20a%20party%20representing%20Hindus.%20Jagan%2C%20however%2C%20has%20no%20other%20alternative.%20He%20left%20the%20Congress%20party%20of%20which%20he%20was%20a%20part%20and%20then%20landed%20up%20in%20jail%20for%20cases%20filed%20against%20him.%20Out%20of%20jail%2C%20the%20cases%20filed%20against%20him%20still%20persist.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20cases%20filed%20by%20CBI%20are%20for%20amassing%20disproportionate%20assets%20through%20misusing%20powers%20when%20his%20father%20Y.S.%20Rajasekhara%20Reddy%20was%20the%20chief%20minister%20of%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%20The%20CBI%20controlled%20by%20the%20Union%20government%20is%20under%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20the%20battle%20for%20the%20South%20heats%20up%2C%20the%20BJP%20which%20has%20very%20little%20presence%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20wants%20to%20use%20Jagan%E2%80%99s%20party.%20The%20BJP%20earlier%20%E2%80%93%20since%20the%20time%20of%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20%E2%80%93%20was%20aligned%20with%20the%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%20(TDP)%20controlled%20by%20Chandrababu%20Naidu.%20But%20at%20the%20end%20of%202018%2C%20Naidu%20suddenly%20broke%20his%20partnership%20with%20the%20BJP%20leaving%20the%20saffron%20party%20high%20and%20dry.%20Many%20perceive%20that%20this%20was%20because%20Naidu%20had%20prime%20ministerial%20dreams%20that%20he%20wanted%20to%20achieve%20without%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20help.%20Naidu%2C%20however%2C%20assigned%20other%20reasons%20for%20breaking%20up%20the%20alliance%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%20contending%20that%20a%20special%20status%20promised%20for%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20was%20no%20longer%20forthcoming.%20The%20special%20status%20would%20mean%20more%20funds%20for%20the%20state.%20Whatever%20be%20the%20case%20in%20the%20changed%20circumstances%2C%20BJP%20was%20forced%20to%20tie%20up%20with%20Jagan%E2%80%99s%20outfit.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0In%20the%20meantime%2C%20Jagan%2C%20aware%20of%20the%20electoral%20battle%20that%20he%20will%20be%20pitted%20in%20against%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20(and%20now%20his%20sister%20Sharmila)%20is%20delivering%20many%20subsidies%20to%20the%20electorate.%20His%20government%20does%20not%20have%20the%20means%20to%20deliver%20all%20of%20them%20to%20the%20public%20due%20to%20lack%20on%20funds.%20But%20he%20is%20depending%20on%20largesse%20from%20the%20Union%20government%20to%20deliver%20the%20goods.%20Naidu%20who%20was%20the%20chief%20minister%20between%202014%20and%202019%20is%20depending%20on%20his%20work%20in%20his%20term%20as%20also%20caste%20equations%20to%20bring%20him%20back%20to%20power.%20Some%20sections%20of%20the%20population%20favour%20Naidu%20strongly.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705027850000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F12081822%2FUntitled-design-11-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fjagan-sharmila-chandrababu-naidu-tdp-ysr-congress-andhra%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20the%20battle%20for%20the%20South%20heats%20up%2C%20the%20BJP%20which%20has%20very%20little%20presence%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20wants%20to%20use%20Jagan%E2%80%99s%20party.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fjagan-sharmila-chandrababu-naidu-tdp-ysr-congress-andhra%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20possible%20bad%20omen%20for%20Trump%2C%20his%20NY%20fraud%20judge%20asked%20the%20AG's%20lawyers%20to%20compare%20him%20to%20Madoff%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bernie%20Madoff%2C%20left.%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20right.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a0994f43bb77284b9c83ad%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221501%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBernie%20Madoff%2C%20left.%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20right.%20Who's%20the%20bigger%20fraudster%2C%20Trump's%20New%20York%20fraud-trial%20judge%20asked%20Thursday.%3Cp%3EReuters%20file%20photos%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ETrump's%20fraud-trial%20judge%20asked%20a%20pointed%20question%20during%20the%20New%20York%20AG's%20closings%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BHow%20would%20you%20compare%20the%20fraud%20you're%20alleging%20to%20the%20Madoff%20Ponzi%20scheme%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20smaller%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20lawyer%20for%20the%20AG%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20both%20cases%20demonstrate%20a%20sense%20of%20entitlement.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20possible%20bad%20omen%20for%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20the%20judge%20in%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrumps-ny-fraud-trial-opens-today-heres-why-still-matters-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20his%20New%20York%20fraud%20trial%20%3C%2Fa%3Einterrupted%20Thursday's%20closing%20arguments%20to%20ask%20a%20lawyer%20for%20the%20New%20York%20attorney%20general's%20office%20to%20compare%20him%20to%20Bernie%20Madoff.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20often%20say%20I%20don't%20enforce%20morality%2C%20I%20enforce%20the%20law%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20judge%20presiding%20over%20the%20three-month%20non-jury%20trial%2C%20New%20York%20Supreme%20Court%20Justice%20Arthur%20Engoron%2C%20said%20at%20the%20end%20of%20day-long%20closing%20arguments%20%E2%80%94%20which%20included%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%