along%20its%20border%20with%20China%20and%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20particular%20EOA%20in%20the%20Shan%20State%2C%20has%2C%20inch%20by%20inch%2C%20been%20grabbing%20key%20trading%20towns%20of%20Myanmar%20with%20China.%20Myanmar%E2%80%99s%20longest%20border%20with%20China%20is%20along%20the%20Shan%20State.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20those%20little%20conquests%20by%20the%20EOA%20were%20unabashedly%20aimed%20at%20pushing%20out%20the%20Junta%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fkokang-laukkaing-laukkai-cyberscam-shan-state-6d5c00eb75d8b6f5aa257c3cdfa68970%5C%22%3ELaukkaing%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20town%20that%20rolls%20in%20the%20biggest%20pile%20of%20hard%20currency%20in%20the%20entire%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESignificantly%2C%20responding%20to%20the%20Junta%E2%80%99s%20surrender%20to%20the%20EOA%20forces%20in%20Kokang%2C%20Junta%20spokesman%20Zaw%20Min%20Tun%20had%20told%20the%20local%20media%20outlet%2C%20%3Cem%3EPopular%20News%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0%3Cem%3EJournal%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20such%20a%20step%20was%20taken%20just%20to%20maintain%20relations%20with%20China.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20regime%20is%20under%20pressure%20from%20China%20to%20restore%20stability%20along%20the%20border%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.irrawaddy.com%2Fnews%2Fburma%2Fmndaa-liberates-kokang-from-myanmar-junta.html%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Irrawaddy%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20a%20number%20of%20Chinese%20citizens%20in%20Yunnan%20were%20injured%20by%20the%20artillery%20fired%20by%20the%20Junta%20at%20the%20EOA%20forces%20during%20the%20Kokang%20offensive%2C%20and%20that%20at%20its%20heels%2C%20top%20Chinese%20diplomats%20had%20a%20closed%20door%20meeting%20with%20the%20Junta%20chief%2C%20Min%20Aung%20Hlaing%2C%20at%20Naypyidaw%2C%20were%20seen%20as%20triggers%20behind%20the%20military%20ejecting%20from%20Kokang.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%20the%20fall%20of%20Kokang%2C%20particularly%20Laukkaing%2C%20there%20is%20more%20to%20it%20than%20just%20China%E2%80%99s%20anger%20at%20the%20Junta%20guns%20injuring%20its%20nationals%20in%20Yunnan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20compelling%20reason%20behind%20the%20Chinese%20establishment%E2%80%99s%20readiness%20to%20back%20the%20EAO%20in%20the%20Shan%20State%20rather%20than%20the%20Junta%20to%20take%20control%20of%20Kokang%20is%20that%20Laukkaing%20had%20become%20a%20seedy%20town%2C%20which%20the%20Asian%20giant%20would%20rather%20not%20have%20on%20its%20southern%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20Laukkaing%20has%20proved%20to%20be%20a%20curse%20for%20a%20large%20number%20of%20people%20from%20China%20as%20well%20as%20for%20many%20from%20other%20South%20and%20East%20Asian%20nations%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20significantly%2C%20the%20China-backed%20fall%20of%20Laukkaing%20may%20also%20end%20up%20bringing%20home%20hundreds%20of%20Indians%20trapped%20in%20that%20township.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhich%20EAO%20has%20taken%20control%20of%20Laukkaing%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20getting%20down%20to%20the%20Chinese%20interest%20in%20a%20change%20of%20guard%20at%20Laukkaing%2C%20lets%20first%20focus%20on%20the%20EAO%20that%20took%20control%20of%20it%20from%20the%20Junta%20forces%20on%20January%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELaukkaing%20was%20surrendered%20to%20the%20Myanmar%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20Army%20(MNDAA)%2C%20a%20Kokang-based%20militia%2C%20which%20had%20joined%20the%20pro-democracy%20Brotherhood%20Alliance.%20The%20other%20two%20EAOs%20are%20the%20Arakan%20Army%20based%20in%20the%20Rakhine%20State%2C%20and%20the%20Ta%E2%80%99ang%20National%20Liberation%20Army%2C%20based%20in%20the%20northern%20part%20of%20the%20Shan%20State.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMNDAA%20was%20an%20outfit%20once%20commanded%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthediplomat.com%2F2022%2F03%2Fpeng-jiasheng-myanmars-king-of-kokang-remembered-with-lavish-funeral%2F%5C%22%3EPeng%20Jiasheng%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20name%20both%20dreaded%20and%20revered%20in%20the%20Kokang%20region.%20This%20recent%20attempt%20of%20MNDAA%20to%20take%20over%20Laukkaing%20was%20its%20second%20since%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20was%20Peng%20Jiasheng%3F%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOften%20termed%20the%20%E2%80%98king%E2%80%99%20of%20Kokang%2C%20Peng%20was%20of%20Chinese%20descent.%20He%20passed%20away%20in%20February%202022%2C%20aged%2091.%20He%20was%20particularly%20noticed%20in%20the%201980s%20as%20a%20leader%20of%20the%20China-backed%20Burmese%20Communist%20Party%20before%20deciding%20to%20break%20out%20of%20it%20to%20build%20his%20own%20militia%2C%20the%20MNDAA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20remembered%20across%20Kokang%20as%20its%20virtual%20ruler%20once%2C%20the%20prime%20peddler%20of%20opium.%20According%20to%20noted%20Asia%20watcher%20Bertil%20Lintner%2C%20Peng%20had%20set%20up%20the%20first%20opium%20factory%20at%20Kokang%20in%20the%201970s%20and%20controlled%20trafficking%20of%20the%20drug%20in%20that%20route.%20An%20extremely%20poor%20region%2C%20residents%20of%20Kokang%20make%20a%20living%20by%20growing%20poppy%3B%20Kokang%20is%20one%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20largest%20producers%20of%20opium.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPeng%E2%80%99s%20death%20in%202022%20dealt%20a%20significant%20blow%20to%20the%20MNDAA.%20His%20loyalists%20organised%20a%20lavish%20funeral%20in%20Mong%20La%2C%20a%20small%20town%20in%20Kokang%20where%20he%20had%20passed%20away.%20All%20top%20militia%20leaders%2C%20along%20with%20representatives%20from%20the%20Chinese%20and%20Myanmar%20governments%2C%20attended%20the%20funeral.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Diplomat%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthediplomat.com%2F2022%2F03%2Fpeng-jiasheng-myanmars-king-of-kokang-remembered-with-lavish-funeral%2F%5C%22%3Ehad%20written%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20%E2%80%9CAmong%20the%20rota%20of%20high-profile%20visitors%20at%20the%20funeral%20were%20Tun%20Myat%20Naing%2C%20the%20head%20of%20the%20Arakan%20Army%2C%20as%20well%20as%20leaders%20from%20the%20Shan%20State%20Army%2C%20the%20Karenni%20Nationalities%20Defence%20Force%2C%20the%20Ta-ang%20National%20Liberation%20Army%2C%20and%20Kachin%20Independence%20Army.%20There%20were%20also%20Chinese%20government%20representatives%20and%20the%20top%20commander%20of%20the%20Myanmar%20military%E2%80%99s%20Kengtung-based%20Golden%20Triangle%20Command%2C%20despite%20the%20military%20currently%20being%20engaged%20in%20hostilities%20with%20the%20MNDAA%20further%20north.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20further%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CLittle%20known%20outside%20Myanmar%20and%20China%2C%20Peng%20(Pheung%20Kya-Shin%20in%20Burmese)%20has%20for%20decades%20been%20an%20integral%20player%20in%20the%20fluid%20conflict%20economies%20of%20Myanmar%E2%80%99s%20Shah%20State.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20added%20to%20Laukkaing%E2%80%99s%20fame%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPeng%20is%20particularly%20remembered%20in%20Kokang%20for%20making%20Laukkaing%20a%20name%20to%20reckon%20with.%20He%20went%20on%20to%20transform%20Laukkaing%20from%20a%20nondescript%2C%20poor%2C%20dusty%20settlement%20along%20China%E2%80%99s%20Yunnan%20Province%20into%20a%20major%20gambling%20hub.%20His%20aim%20was%20to%20offer%20the%20rich%20Chinese%20a%20casino%20town%20in%20the%20neighbourhood%20since%20gambling%20was%2Fis%20a%20banned%20activity%20in%20that%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHordes%20came%20down%20to%20Laukkaing%20from%20across%20the%20border.%20In%20the%20course%20of%20time%2C%20the%20glitzy%20casinos%20and%20hotels%20set%20up%20in%20Laukkaing%20with%20Peng%20and%20his%20warlord%20allies%E2%80%99%20drug%20money%20succeeded%20in%20enticing%20gamblers%20from%20other%20Asian%20countries.%20Peng%E2%80%99s%20militia%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20also%20succeeded%20in%20spreading%20its%20tentacles%20to%20other%20lucrative%20businesses%20across%20East%20Asian%20nations%20like%20Laos%2C%20Cambodia%2C%20etc.%2C%20including%20illegal%20mining.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20time%2C%20Laukkaing%20transformed%20into%20a%20bustling%20town%20with%20high%20rises%2C%20emerging%20as%20a%20major%20gambling%20destination%20in%20that%20part%20of%20Asia%2C%20generating%20billions%20every%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20around%202009%2C%20Peng%20fell%20into%20trouble.%20He%20had%20to%20temporarily%20flee%20to%20China%20after%20falling%20out%20with%20Myanmar%E2%80%99s%20Junta%20for%20refusing%20to%20support%20it%20against%20the%20pro-democracy%20forces%2C%20including%20Aung%20San%20Suu%20Kyi%E2%80%99s%20party.%20Junta%20chief%20Min%20Aung%20Hlaing%20ordered%20raids%20at%20Peng%E2%80%99s%20house%20in%20a%20drug%20trafficking%20case%2C%20and%20convinced%20his%20deputy%20Bia%20Suocheng%20to%20turn%20against%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Junta%E2%80%99s%20support%2C%20Bia%20succeeded%20in%20snatching%20away%20Peng%E2%80%99s%20multi-crore%20casino%20business.%20Still%2C%20a%20considerable%20number%20of%20MNDAA%20leaders%20continued%20their%20support%20to%20an%20ageing%20Peng.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20Bia%2C%20who%20was%20joined%20in%20by%20some%20other%20warlords%20of%20Chinese%20origin%2C%20Laukkaing%20also%20became%20notorious%20for%20money%20laundering%20and%20human%20trafficking%2C%20not%20just%20from%20China%20but%20from%20across%20several%20Asian%20nations%2C%20including%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fchin-state-operation-1027-myanmar-mizoram%5C%22%3ERecent%20Developments%20in%20Chin%20State%20Raise%20More%20Questions%20on%20New%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20Approach%20Towards%20Myanmar%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20did%20China%20back%20MNDAA%20in%20seizing%20Laukkaing%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20time%2C%20the%20warlords%20in%20control%20of%20Laukkaing%E2%80%99s%20gambling%20business%20extended%20their%20operations%20to%20include%20Internet%20fraud.%20It%20lured%20hundreds%20of%20IT%20professionals%20to%20Laukkaing%20promising%20better%20employment.%20On%20arrival%20though%2C%20they%20would%20be%20illegally%20detained%2C%20with%20their%20passports%20confiscated.%20They%20would%20be%20forced%20to%20work%20at%20the%20casinos%20and%20carry%20out%20Internet%20frauds%20across%20the%20world.%20Those%20who%20resisted%20were%20beaten%20up%2C%20tortured%20with%20electric%20shocks%2C%20and%20even%20shot%20dead%20if%20seen%20fleeing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%2C%20unable%20to%20put%20a%20stop%20to%20the%20menace%20at%20its%20border%20and%20its%20nationals%20regularly%20falling%20into%20the%20trap%2C%20had%2C%20from%20time%20to%20time%2C%20put%20considerable%20diplomatic%C2%A0pressure%20on%20Myanmar%E2%80%99s%20Junta%20to%20clamp%20down%20on%20the%20criminal%20elements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20at%20times%2C%20the%20Junta%20had%20handed%20over%20to%20the%20Chinese%20Police%20scamsters%20wanted%20in%20that%20country%2C%20its%20deep%20links%20with%20the%20warlords%20at%20Laukkaing%2C%20who%20run%20those%20online%20scam%20centres%2C%20had%20come%20in%20the%20way%20of%20doing%20anything%20drastic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20those%20warlords%20were%20Junta%20allies%2C%20they%20hoped%20to%20be%20protected%20by%20it%20and%20didn%E2%80%99t%20quite%20restrain%20themselves%20from%20defrauding%20the%20Chinese%20nationals%2C%20including%20trafficking%20them%20to%20Kokang.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20by%20backing%20the%20MNDAA%E2%80%99s%20takeover%20of%20Laukkaing%2C%20China%E2%80%99s%20dominion%20over%20the%20gambling%20hub%2C%20and%20the%20lawless%20region%20in%20general%2C%20is%20a%20given.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlready%2C%20several%20top%20family%20members%20of%20Laukkaing%E2%80%99s%20top%20scamsters%20and%20casino%20owners%20have%20been%20handed%20over%20to%20the%20Chinese%20authorities%20by%20the%20local%20administration%20to%20face%20trial.%20According%20to%20some%20reports%2C%20Peng%E2%80%99s%20deputy%20Bai%20had%20scooted%20Laukkaing%20for%20an%20unknown%20place.%20One%20such%20warlord%20of%20Chinese%20descent%20is%20said%20to%20have%20committed%20suicide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELaukkaing%E2%80%99s%20tentacles%20across%20Asia%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftherecord.media%2Frebel-offensive-myanmar-cyber-scam-crackdown%5C%22%3ELaukkaing%20scamsters%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20also%20been%20conning%20people%20from%20other%20Asian%20nations.%20In%20August%202023%2C%20the%20United%20Nations%20Human%20Rights%20Office%2C%20in%20a%20report%2C%20had%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CHundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20people%20are%20being%20forcibly%20engaged%20by%20organised%20criminal%20gangs%20into%20online%20criminality%20in%20Southeast%20Asia%20%E2%80%93%20from%20romance-investment%20scams%20and%20crypto%20fraud%20to%20illegal%20gambling.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPeople%20who%20are%20coerced%20into%20working%20in%20these%20scamming%20operations%20endure%20inhumane%20treatment%20while%20being%20forced%20to%20carry%20out%20crimes.%20They%20are%20victims.%20They%20are%20not%20criminals%2C%E2%80%9D%20UN%20High%20Commissioner%20for%20Human%20Rights%20Volker%20T%C3%BCrk%20said%20in%20that%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%2C%20citing%20data%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ohchr.org%2Fen%2Fpress-releases%2F2023%2F08%2Fhundreds-thousands-trafficked-work-online-scammers-se-asia-says-un-report%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CCredible%20sources%20indicate%20that%20at%20least%20120%2C000%20people%20across%20Myanmar%20may%20be%20held%20in%20situations%20where%20they%20are%20forced%20to%20carry%20out%20online%20scams%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20same%20data%20was%20quoted%20by%20the%20UK%20in%20December%20while%20sanctioning%2014%20individuals%20and%20entities%20connected%20to%20the%20Southeast%20Asia%E2%80%99s%20ever%20expanding%20online%20scamming%20industry%2C%20including%20Myanmar.%20More%20on%20it%20can%20be%20read%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftherecord.