er%20USS%20Carney%20Red%20Sea%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65494b0236d588dc55cbb09d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221334%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUS%20Navy%20guided-missile%20destroyer%20USS%20Carney%20defeats%20a%20combination%20of%20Houthi%20missiles%20and%20drones%20in%20the%20Red%20Sea%20on%20October%2019%2C%202023.%3Cp%3EUS%20Navy%2FMCS2%20Aaron%20Lau%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20US%20and%20UK%C2%A0%20launched%20strikes%20against%20Houthi%20rebels%20in%20Yemen%C2%A0%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20strikes%20come%20after%20repeated%20warnings%20from%20the%20US%20and%20UK%20over%20the%20Houthis'%20attacks%20on%20shipping%20vessels.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Iran-backed%20rebels%20have%20conducted%2027%20attacks%20on%20commercial%20shipping%20since%20mid-November.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%2C%20together%20with%20the%20UK%20and%20with%20the%20support%20of%20other%20allies%2C%20launched%20military%20strikes%20against%20Houthi%20rebels%20in%20Yemen%20in%20an%20effort%20to%20suppress%20the%20group's%20ongoing%20attacks%20on%20commercial%20shipping%20vessels%20in%20key%20waterways.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20US%20defense%20official%20confirmed%20to%20Business%20Insider%20that%20strikes%20were%20launched%20from%20airborne%2C%20surface%2C%20and%20subsurface%20platforms%2C%20specifically%20jets%2C%20ships%2C%20and%20at%20least%20one%20submarine.%20They%20added%20that%20the%20retaliatory%20strikes%20were%20carried%20out%20%26quot%3Bprotect%20US%20and%20international%20shipping%20vessels%20and%20degrade%20Houthi%20capabilities.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20official%20said%20the%20strikes%20targeted%20Houthi%20radar%20stations%20and%20storage%20facilities%20and%20launch%20sites%20for%20drones%2C%20cruise%20missiles%2C%20and%20ballistic%20missiles.%20All%20of%20the%20targets%20hit%20during%20the%20strikes%20are%20%26quot%3Bmilitary%20objectives%26quot%3B%20by%20nature%20and%20are%20located%20in%20areas%20where%20civilians%20are%20not%20assessed%20to%20be%20present%2C%20they%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDegrading%20these%20capabilities%20hinders%20the%20Houthis'%20ability%20to%20continue%20their%20malign%20behavior%20in%20the%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPresident%20Joe%20Biden%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whitehouse.gov%2Fbriefing-room%2Fstatements-releases%2F2024%2F01%2F11%2Fstatement-from-president-joe-biden-on-coalition-strikes-in-houthi-controlled-areas-in-yemen%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estatement%3C%2Fa%3E%20called%20the%20strikes%20%26quot%3Bdefensive%20action%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20he%20%26quot%3Bwill%20not%20hesitate%20to%20direct%20further%20measures%20to%20protect%20our%20people%20and%20the%20free%20flow%20of%20international%20commerce%20as%20necessary.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20strikes%20against%20the%20Houthis%20follow%20repeated%20warnings%20from%20the%20US%20and%20the%20UK%20and%20others%20that%20the%20Iran-backed%20rebels%20would%20face%20consequences%20if%20they%20did%20not%20stop%20attacking%20international%20shipping%20lanes%20off%20the%20coast%20of%20Yemen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20gotten%20to%20the%20point%20where%20all%20other%20approaches%20have%20not%20played%20out%2C%20so%20it's%20time%20to%20let%20the%20Houthis%20know%20they%20can't%20interfere%20with%20international%20trade%20like%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20Mick%20Ryan%2C%20a%20retired%20Major%20General%20in%20the%20Australian%20Army%20and%20a%20military%20strategist%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Jan.%203%2C%20the%20US%20and%20over%20a%20dozen%20allies%20issued%20a%20statement%20condemning%20the%20Houthis%20for%20their%20provocations%2C%20demanding%20an%20end%20to%20the%20attacks%2C%20and%20warning%20them%20against%20further%20incidents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20following%20day%2C%20a%20senior%20Biden%20administration%20official%20told%20reporters%20they%20%26q