ion%20is%20yours%20alone%20%E2%80%94%20the%20individual%20plan%20is%20%2410.99%20per%20month.%20It%20gives%20one%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-id%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EApple%20ID%3C%2Fa%3E%20access%20to%20the%20catalog%20of%20100%20million%20songs%20across%20all%20the%20associated%20Apple%20devices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20want%20to%20share%20your%20Apple%20Music%20account%20with%20your%20partner%20or%20other%20family%20members%2C%20you'll%20want%20the%20Apple%20Music%20Family%20plan%20(%2416.99%20per%20month).%20It%20lets%20up%20to%20six%20people%20share%20a%20single%20subscription.%20Each%20family%20member%20can%20stream%20music%20and%20podcasts%20on%20all%20of%20their%20Apple%20devices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ECan%20you%20look%20someone%20up%20on%20Apple%20Music%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPart%20of%20the%20joy%20of%20music%20is%20discovery%2C%20and%20there's%20nothing%20like%20discovering%20new%20music%20from%20friends%20and%20family.%20Apple%20Music%20lets%20you%20follow%20other%20subscribers%20to%20see%20their%20music.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20two%20ways%20to%20find%20other%20users%20in%20Apple%20Music.%20For%20starters%2C%20you%20can%20browse%20for%20users%20already%20on%20your%20contacts%20list.%20To%20do%20that%2C%20start%20Apple%20Music%20and%20tap%20your%20account%20icon%20at%20the%20top%20right%20of%20the%20page.%20On%20the%20Account%20page%2C%20tap%20%3Cstrong%3EView%20Profile%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20at%20the%20top%20and%20choose%20%3Cstrong%3EFollow%20More%20Friends%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20You'll%20see%20a%20list%20of%20everyone%20you%20know%20(in%20your%20contacts%20list)%20who%20is%20already%20using%20Apple%20Music.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221290%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Apple%20Music%20app%20shows%20Following%20list%20with%20round%20icons%20and%20a%20red%20%26quot%3BFollow%20More%20Friends%26quot%3B%20button%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F659d5c15ec62ab5daf81d665%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221963%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EApple%20Music%20will%20show%20you%20all%20the%20friends%20from%20your%20contacts%20who%20also%20use%20Apple%20Music.%3Cp%3EDave%20Johnson%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20also%20manually%20search%20for%20users.%20Tap%20the%20Search%20icon%20at%20the%20bottom%20right%20of%20the%20Apple%20Music%20screen%20and%2C%20in%20the%20Search%20bar%2C%20type%20the%20name%20of%20the%20person%20you%20are%20looking%20for.%20Tap%20%3Cstrong%3ESearch%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20If%20there%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20results%2C%20you%20might%20want%20to%20filter%20by%20tapping%20%3Cstrong%3EProfiles%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20When%20you%20see%20the%20person%20you're%20looking%20for%2C%20tap%20%3Cstrong%3EFollow%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20person%20you%20request%20to%20follow%20has%20set%20their%20profile%20to%20private%2C%20they%20must%20approve%20your%20request%20before%20you%20start%20following%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EHow%20do%20I%20see%20friend%20requests%20on%20Apple%20Music%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20your%20profile%20is%20private%2C%20you'll%20need%20to%20approve%20friend%20requests%20before%20people%20may%20follow%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpen%20the%20Apple%20Music%20app%2C%20tap%20your%20account%20icon%20at%20the%20top%20right%2C%20then%20%3Cstrong%3EView%20Profile%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20You%20should%20now%20see%20a%20list%20of%20anyone%20who%20wants%20to%20follow%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20don't%20want%20to%20approve%20each%20person%20individually%20and%20prefer%20to%20let%20anyone%20follow%20you%20automatically%2C%20go%20to%20your%20profile%20page%20and%20tap%20%3Cstrong%3EEdit%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20In%20the%20%3Cstrong%3EWho%20Can%20Follow%20Your%20Activity%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20section%2C%20change%20the%20selection%20from%20%3Cstrong%3EPeople%20You%20Approve%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EEveryone%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221290%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Screenshot%20of%20Apple%20Music's%20%26quot%3BEdit%20Profile%26quot%3B%20section%20with%20a%20red%20box%20ticked%20next%20to%20the%20text%20%26quot%3BPeople%20You%20Approve%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F659d5c6fec62ab5daf81d689%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222038%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EYou%20can%20choose%20whether%20you%20need%20to%20approve%20each%20person%20who%20wants%20to%20follow%20you%20in%20Apple%20Music.%3Cp%3EDave%20Johnson%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3ECan%20you%20see%20who%20viewed%20your%20Apple%20Music%20profile%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EApple%20Music%20doesn't%20notify%20users%20if%20someone%20has%20viewed%20their%20profile%20or%20listened%20to%20their%20playlists.%20That%20means%20you%20can%20browse%20other%20people's%20profiles%20in%20search%20of%20new%20music%2C%20and%20they%20won't%20know%20you've%20been%20checking%20out%20their%20tunes.%20The%20reverse%20is%20also%20true%2C%20though%3A%20you%20won't%20be%20notified%20when%20someone%20views%20your%20profile.%20Apple%20Music%20doesn't%20track%20or%20record%20this%20kind%20of%20viewing%20activity%2C%20so%20you%20can't%20later%20go%20back%20and%20see%20who%20viewed%20your%20profile%20or%20your%20music.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ECan%20a%20business%20play%20music%20from%20Apple%20Music%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EUnfortunately%2C%20Apple%20Music%20is%20considered%20a%20consumer%20product%2C%20and%20the%20licensing%20model%20for%20the%20music%20streamed%20by%20the%20service%20is%20for%20private%20and%20non-commercial%20playback.%20That%20doesn't%20allow%20for%20public%20broadcasts%20in%20a%20business%20setting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20operate%20a%20business%20and%20want%20to%20stream%20music%20to%20clients%2C%20customers%2C%20or%20employees%2C%20you%20should%20instead%20consider%20a%20music%20streaming%20service%20for%20business.%20Options%20include%20SiriusXM%20for%20Business%20and%20Soundtrack%20Your%20Brand%2C%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EHow%20do%20Spotify%20and%20Apple%20music%20compare%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EApple%20Music%20and%20Spotify%20are%20more%20alike%20than%20they%20are%20different.%20They're%20both%20subscription%20music%20streaming%20platforms%20offering%20a%20vast%20library%20of%20tunes%20and%20podcasts%3B%20you%20can%20listen%20on%20your%20phone%20and%20other%20devices.%20But%20if%20you're%20trying%20to%20decide%20between%20the%20two%2C%20consider%20the%20details.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20platforms%20have%20several%20service%20tiers%2C%20but%20only%20Spotify%20makes%20it%20possible%20to%20listen%20for%20free%20with%20an%20ad-supported%20introductory%20tier.%20From%20there%2C%20Apple%20Music%20and%20Spotify%20have%20standard%20subscriptions%20for%20%2410.99%20per%20month%20and%20discounted%20%245.99%20per%20month%20student%20plans.%20There's%20no%20price%20advantage%20for%20either%20service%20aside%20from%20Spotify's%20free%20tier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20sound%20quality%2C%20Apple%20has%20an%20edge.%20Apple%20Music's%20entire%20catalog%20is%20encoded%20at%20resolutions%20from%2016-bit%2F44.1kHz%20(CD-quality)%20to%2024-bit%2F192kHz%20(generally%20considered%20hi-res).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpotify%2C%20in%20comparison%2C%20has%20encoded%20its%20catalog%20at%20resolutions%20ranging%20from%2096kbps%20to%20160kbps%20to%20320kbps.%20None%20of%20those%20quite%20equal%20CD%20quality%2C%20much%20less%20hi-res.%20Customers%20have%20waited%20for%20the%20platform%20to%20offer%20a%20premium%20hi-res%20tier%20for%20several%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApple%20also%20claims%20a%20small%20advantage%20regarding%20the%20size%20of%20the%20song%20catalog.%20Spotify%20has%20over%2080%20million%20tracks%2C%20while%20Apple%20Music%20has%20about%2020%25%20more%2C%20or%20over%20100%20million%20songs.%20But%20because%20all%20the%20most%20common%20and%20popular%20artists%20are%20fully%20represented%20in%20both%20catalogs%2C%20you%20might%20not%20notice%20a%20difference%20unless%20y