an%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%B5g%2Fm%3Csup%3E3%3C%2Fsup%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20during%20a%20portion%20of%20the%20study%20period.%20The%20permissible%20limit%20in%20India%2C%20as%20mentioned%20earlier%2C%20is%2060%20%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%B5g%2Fm%3Csup%3E3%3C%2Fsup%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E.%20Researchers%20attribute%20the%20poor%20air%20quality%20to%20a%20combination%20of%20human-related%20and%20natural%20factors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20study%20revealed%20that%20calm%20winds%2C%20weak%20mixing%20conditions%2C%20temperature%20inversion%2C%20and%20a%20shallow%20planetary%20boundary%20layer%20are%20responsible%20for%20exacerbating%20the%20impact%20of%20widespread%20biomass%20fuel%20burning%20in%20winters%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20presence%20of%20transport%20exhaust%20and%20particulate%20matter%20carried%20from%20distant%20regions%20by%20westerlies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20study%2C%20%E2%80%98Particulate%20Pollution%20over%20an%20urban%20Himalayan%20site%3A%20Temporal%20variability%2C%20impact%20of%20meteorology%20and%20potential%20source%20regions%E2%80%99%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2F34371409%2F%5C%22%3Epublished%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%3Cem%3E%20Science%20of%20the%20Total%20Environment%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20is%20authored%20by%20professor%20Shakil%20Romshoo%2C%20%3Cspan%3EMudasir%20Ahmad%20Bhat%3Cspan%3E%2C%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EGufran%20Beig.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20delves%20deep%20into%20the%20status%20and%20causes%20of%20air%20pollution%20in%20Srinagar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMass%20concentration%20of%20PM2.5%20and%20PM10%20in%20Srinagar%2C%20our%20study%20revealed%2C%20is%20higher%20than%20other%20high-altitude%20sites%20in%20Hindu%20Kush%20Himalayas%2C%E2%80%9D%20Romshoo%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20poor%20air%20quality%20is%20a%20major%20concern%20for%20people%20with%20respiratory%20ailments.%20This%20has%20led%20medical%20professionals%20to%20call%20for%20stronger%20and%20consistent%20efforts%20to%20curtail%20controllable%20sources%20of%20pollutants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20published%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Lancet%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20J%26amp%3BK%20was%20among%20the%20top%20four%20regions%20for%20chronic%20obstructive%20pulmonary%20disease%20(COPD)%2C%20with%20over%204%2C700%20people%20suffering%20from%20this%20respiratory%20disorder%20per%20lakh%20of%20the%20population.%20This%20number%20is%20twice%20as%20high%20as%20in%20most%20Indian%20states.%20COPD%20is%20also%20among%20the%20leading%20causes%20of%20death%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thelancet.com%2Fjournals%2Flanglo%2Farticle%2FPIIS2214-109X(18)30409-1%2Ffulltext%5C%22%3Etitled%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%98Burden%20of%20Chronic%20Respiratory%20Diseases%20and%20their%20heterogeneity%20across%20the%20states%20of%20India%3A%20the%20global%20burden%20of%20disease%20study%201990-2016%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProfessor%20Parvaiz%20A.%20Koul%2C%20pulmonologist%20and%20an%20avid%20researcher%2C%20was%20one%20of%20the%20contributing%20authors%20to%20this%20study.%20Currently%2C%20he%E2%80%99s%20the%20director%20of%20Sher-i-Kashmir%20Institute%20of%20Medical%20Sciences.%20He%20said%20that%20every%20winter%2C%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20hospitals%20face%20a%20deluge%20of%20patients%20with%20respiratory%20distress%20and%20ailments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20the%20highest%20prevalence%20of%20chronic%20airflow%20limitation%20in%20India%3A%20one%20in%20every%20five%20individuals%20over%20the%20age%20of%2040%20years%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9CSmoking%20and%20air%20pollution%20are%20known%20contributing%20factors%2C%20although%20we%20need%20more%20research%20in%20these%20areas%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKoul%20said%20that%20there%20may%20be%20a%20genetic%20factor%2C%20but%20genes%20could%20not%20be%20altered.%20Therefore%2C%20we%20need%20to%20work%20on%20external%20factors.%20%E2%80%9CDomestic%20and%20ambient%20air%20quality%20are%20the%20keys.%20Anything%20that%20pollutes%20the%20air%20needs%20to%20be%20addressed%20and%20addressed%20on%20priority%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EData%20from%20the%20Department%20of%20Road%20Transport%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20reveals%20that%20the%20vehicle%20population%20in%20Srinagar%20is%20approximately%204%20lakh%2C%20excluding%20vehicles%20from%20other%20districts%2C%20states%2C%20and%20those%20owned%20by%20the%20armed%20forces.%20The%20rate%20of%20increase%20in%20the%20number%20of%20vehicles%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20over%20the%20past%20five%20years%20has%20been%20unprecedented.%20Between%202012%20and%202017%2C%20there%20were%204%2C78%2C292%20new%20vehicle%20registrations%2C%20and%20this%20number%20surged%20to%207%2C84%2C503%20between%202017%20and%202022.%20According%20to%20the%20National%20Family%20Health%20Survey-5%2C%2024%25%20of%20households%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20own%20a%20car%2C%20the%20second-highest%20after%20Kerala.%20The%20dismal%20public%20transport%20situation%20necessitates%20the%20reliance%20on%20and%20usage%20of%20private%20transportation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20an%20official%20from%20the%20Motor%20Vehicles%20Department%2C%20who%20requested%20anonymity%2C%20there%20is%20a%20shortage%20of%202%20lakh%20public%20transport%20seats%20per%20day%20in%20Srinagar.%20The%20emissions%20from%20the%20congested%20roads%20in%20Srinagar%2C%20caused%20by%20the%20ever-growing%20use%20of%20privately%20owned%20fossil%20fuel-burning%20vehicles%2C%20are%20paving%20the%20way%20for%20a%20potential%20health%20and%20environmental%20catastrophe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20study%20on%20particulate%20pollution%20by%20Romshoo%20advocates%20a%20strict%20check%20on%20emissions%20from%20coal%20burning%2C%20dusty%20roads%2C%20wood%20burning%2C%20and%20vehicular%20traffic.%20It%20calls%20for%20the%20utilisation%20of%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20hydroelectric%20potential%20to%20replace%20fossil%20fuels%20and%20wood%20burning%20in%20winters.%20However%2C%20Kashmir%20faces%20acute%20power%20shortages%20that%20get%20worse%20in%20winters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr.%20Naveed%20Nazir%20Shah%2C%20head%20of%20the%20pulmonology%20department%20at%20the%20Chest%20Diseases%20Hospital%20in%20Srinagar%2C%20said%20that%20power%20shortages%20force%20people%20to%20use%20wood%20and%20coal-based%20heating%20in%20their%20homes%2C%20contributing%20to%20indoor%20air%20pollution.%20Furthermore%2C%20individuals%20relying%20on%20oxygen%20therapy%20face%20challenges%20as%20they%20do%20not%20receive%20round-the-clock%20electricity%20to%20operate%20the%20essential%20oxygen%20concentrators%20they%20depend%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20the%20patient%20number%20has%20been%20increasing%20threefold%20every%20winter.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20infections%2C%20the%20allergies%2C%20the%20COPD%2C%20everything%20worsens%20with%20cold%20and%20the%20smog%20that%20we%20have%20in%20Srinagar.%20The%20power%20shortages%20are%20also%20affecting%20us%20in%20many%20ways%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704980044000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F11165359%2Fimage-1719.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fsrinagars-air-quality-how-vehicle-pollution-and-power-shortages-have-been-worsening-the-issue%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20prolonged%20poor%20air%20quality%20in%20Srinagar%20during%20the%20winter%20months%2C%20spanning%20November%20to%20February%2C%20has%20been%20a%20consistent%20concern%20for%20the%20past%20decade.%20Studies%20attribute%20the%20issue%20to%20a%20combination%20of%20human-related%20and%20natural%20factors%2C%20including%20biomass%20fuel%20burning.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fsrinagars-air-quality-how-vehicle-pollution-and-power-shortages-have-been-worsening-the-issue%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trio%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Uber%20for%20Healthcare%E2%80%99%20Aims%20to%20Make%20Hospital%20Visits%20Easier%20in%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20Sunil%20(name%20changed)%20from%20Thiruvananthapuram%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20multiple%20anterior%20lipomas%20%E2%80%94%20fatty%20lumps%20that%20appear%20on%20the%20neck%2C%20chest%20and%20shoulders%2C%20he%20was%20told%20they%20would%20need%20surgical%20excision.%20Needless%20to%20say%2C%20he%20was%20worried.%20He%20pictured%20the%20tough%20road%20that%20lay%20ahead%20%E2%80%94%20contacting%20a%20good%20surgeon%2C%20getting%20his%20insurance%20papers%20ready%2C%20and%20of%20course%2C%20the%20anxiety%20that%20accompanies%20the%20above.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESunil%20is%20fine%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsk%20him%20about%20his%20experience%2C%20and%20he%20recalls%20it%20to%20be%20one%20of%20the%20most%20seamless%20and%20affordable%20he%20has%20had.%20He%20credits%20a%20Kerala-based%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F332843%2Fdr-pal-palaniappan-manickam-medical-comedy-show-weight-loss-intermittent-fasting-health-tips-standup-comedian%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehealthcare%20startup%20%3C%2Fa%3Efor%20his%20calm%20nerves%20throughout%20the%20procedure%20and%20even%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cofounder%20of%20Mykare%20Health%2C%20Senu%20Sam%20is%20elated%20when%20he%20hears%20stories%20like%20these.%20He%20sees%20it%20as%20a%20culmination%20of%20the%20goals%20of%20the%20startup%2C%20which%20was%20launched%20to%20provide%20people%20in%20South%20Indian%20Tier%201%20and%202%20cities%20with%20access%20to%20hassle-free%20services%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20planned%2C%20non-emergency%20surgeries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20startup%20does%20this%20through%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F332795%2Fhistory-medical-doctors-professors-trailblazers-shaped-indian-medicine-cure-for-epilepsy-malaria-contraception%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eunique%20model%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20takes%20care%20of%20the%20patient%E2%80%99s%20needs%20from%20the%20first%20to%20the%20last%20touch%20point%2C%20ensuring%20they%20are%20in%20good%20hands.%20Recovery%20and%20rest%20must%20be%20the%20only%20things%20on%20the%20patient%E2%80%99s%20mind%2C%20they%20believe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20catches%20up%20with%20Senu%20and%20the%20co-founders%20Rahmathulla%20T%20M%20and%20Joash%20Philipose%20%E2%80%94%20all%20in%20their%20mid-30s%20and%20hailing%20from%20Kerala%20%E2%80%94%20it%20is%20fascinating%20to%20note%20how%20personal%20experience%20intertwined%20with%20their%20tech%20prowess%20led%20them%20to%20launch%20a%20one-of-a-kind%20healthcare%20initiative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ENecessity%20is%20the%20mother%20of%20invention%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20stint%20of%2013%20years%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F331526%2Fpune-startup-innovates-ai-based-technology-screen-tuberculosis-within-seconds-innovation-in-healthcare%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehealthcare%20space%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20head%20of%20sales%2C%20introduced%20Senu%20to%20two%20things%20%E2%80%94%20a%20blaring%20need%20for%20introducing%20tech%20into%20the%20sector%20and%20two%20people%20who%20shared%20his%20mindset.%20Oblivious%20that%20one%20of%20them%20would%20rise%20to%20CTO%20at%20Mykare%20and%20the%20other%20would%20share%20his%20expertise%20as%20chief%20product%20officer%2C%20they%20became%20fast%20friends.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYears%20later%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eas%20they%20bend%20their%20heads%20together%20over%20ideas%20of%20scaling%20Mykare%20Health%2C%20Senu%20says%20their%20expertise%20is%20unparalleled.%3C%2F