platform.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20pre-medical%20counselling%20team%20will%20then%20call%20the%20patient%20to%20understand%20their%20requirements%20and%20then%20pass%20the%20patient%20details%20to%20the%20medical%20counselling%20team.%20This%20team%20will%20call%20the%20patient%20to%20ease%20them%20of%20any%20worries%20regarding%20the%20surgery.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenu%20came%20across%20a%20report%20that%20suggested%20that%2070%20percent%20of%20patients%20do%20not%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F296533%2Fdoctors-innovate-tele-icu-for-critical-care-patients-cloudphysician-health-and-medicine%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eundergo%20surgery%3C%2Fa%3E%20because%20of%20the%20fear%20of%20it.%20%E2%80%9CThese%20fears%20are%20because%20of%20several%20things.%20We%20want%20to%20ease%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20Senu%20emphasises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20patient%E2%80%99s%20documents%20and%20reports%20are%20in%20place%2C%20a%20consultation%20is%20arranged%20with%20the%20doctor%20who%20will%20be%20performing%20the%20surgery.%20Rahmathulla%20explains%20that%20to%20add%20a%20personal%20touch%20to%20the%20digital%20platform%2C%20they%20have%20introduced%20dedicated%20care%20coordinators%20%E2%80%98KareBuddy%E2%80%99%20within%20the%20Mykare%20Health%20ecosystem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20individuals%20become%20reliable%20points%20of%20contact%2C%20offering%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F288209%2Ffibroheal-bandage-broken-silk-cocoon-fast-wound-healing-innovation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epersonalised%20guidance%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20support%20throughout%20the%20treatment.%20Acting%20as%20advocates%20for%20the%20patients%2C%20they%20assist%20with%20appointment%20scheduling%2C%20clarify%20medical%20information%2C%20and%20ensure%20seamless%20coordination%20among%20healthcare%20providers.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5C