)%20%E2%80%98Hey%20Ram%E2%80%99%20is%20written.%20Today%20that%20Ram%20Rajya%20is%20being%20started%20with%20the%20Pran%20Pratishtha%20and%20Congress%20is%20not%20attending.%20This%20makes%20it%20very%20clear%20the%20difference%20between%20Nehru%E2%80%99s%20Congress%20and%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20Congress%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Trivedi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20released%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20Congress%20had%20said%20that%20its%20leaders%20%E2%80%93%20party%20chief%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20his%20predecessor%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20and%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20Lok%20Sabha%20leader%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%20%E2%80%93%20who%20received%20the%20invitation%2C%20declined%20the%20invitation%20calling%20it%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbreaking-congress-declines-invitation-to-ram-temple-inauguration-calls-its-clearly-an-rss-bjp-event%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CRSS%2FBJP%20event%3C%2Fa%3E.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwhy-congress-clearly-saying-january-22-is-part-of-rss-bjps-political-project-matters%5C%22%3EWhy%20Congress%20Clearly%20Saying%20January%2022%20Is%20Part%20of%20RSS%2FBJP%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Political%20Project%E2%80%99%20Matters%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CReligion%20is%20a%20personal%20matter.%20But%20the%20RSS%2FBJP%20have%20long%20made%20a%20political%20project%20of%20the%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya.%20The%20inauguration%20of%20the%20incomplete%20temple%20by%20the%20leaders%20of%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20RSS%20has%20been%20obviously%20brought%20forward%20for%20electoral%20gain%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20statement%20from%20Congress%E2%80%99%20general%20secretary%20media%20in-charge%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20had%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnion%20minister%20for%20parliamentary%20affairs%20Pralhad%20Joshi%20accused%20the%20party%20of%20%E2%80%9Cappeasement%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Copposing%20Hindu%20beliefs%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20the%20sake%20of%20appeasement%2C%20the%20Congress%20party%20is%20continuously%20opposing%20Hindu%20beliefs%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnd%20now%20in%20more%20than%2030-40%20years%20whenever%20the%20issue%20of%20Ram%20Temple%20has%20been%20raised%20they%20have%20either%20ridiculed%20or%20opposed%20it.%20They%20filed%20an%20appeal%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20in%20which%20they%20questioned%20the%20existence%20of%20Lord%20Ram%20and%20questioned%20the%20Ram%20Setu.%20The%20Congress%20party%20has%20reached%20the%20heights%20of%20appeasement%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnion%20Minister%20for%20Women%20and%20Child%20Development%20Smriti%20Irani%20on%20Wednesday%20night%20said%20that%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Canti-Ram%E2%80%9D%20face%20has%20become%20apparent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCongress%20party%E2%80%99s%20anti-Lord%20Ram%20face%20is%20before%20the%20nation.%20It%20is%20no%20surprise%20that%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20Sonia%20Gandhi%2C%20the%20party%20that%20had%20filed%20an%20affidavit%20before%20the%20court%20that%20Lord%20Ram%20does%20not%20have%20an%20identity.%20Under%20the%20leadership%20of%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20and%20Congress%2C%20INDI%20Alliance%20has%20insulted%20Sanatan%20Dharma%20time%20and%20again.%20Now%2C%20the%20declining%20of%20the%20invitation%20to%20the%20%E2%80%98pran%20pratishtha%E2%80%99%20ceremony%20shows%20their%20anti-Sanatan%20mindset%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Irani%20on%20Wednesday%20night%20to%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FWATCH%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23WATCH%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20On%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20%26amp%3B%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%20declining%20the%20invitation%20to%20%E2%80%98pranpratishtha%E2%80%99%20ceremony%20of%20Ram%2