rganisations%20have%20accused%20the%20state%20government%20under%20chief%20minister%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%20of%20%E2%80%9Copening%20a%20new%20front%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20ongoing%20violence%20after%20Singh%20said%20that%20his%20government%20is%20considering%20setting%20up%20a%20committee%20to%20rethink%20the%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20status%20of%20the%20Kukis%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fpolitical-pulse%2Fkukis-cm-biren-singh-new-front-escalate-conflict-govt-rethink-st-status-9103934%2F%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAny%20such%20attempts%20to%20%E2%80%9Cuse%20the%20state%20machinery%20to%20target%E2%80%9D%20their%20community%20will%20further%20escalate%20the%20conflict%2C%20they%20warned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESingh%E2%80%99s%20statement%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20January%209%2C%20came%20in%20response%20to%20queries%20on%20a%20representation%20made%20to%20the%20Union%20ministry%20of%20tribal%20affairs%20by%20the%20Meitei%20leader%20of%20the%20Republican%20Party%20of%20India%20(Athawale)%2C%20Maheshwar%20Thounaojam%2C%20for%20the%20exclusion%20of%20Kukis%20from%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20ST%20list.%20Thounaojam%20holds%20the%20view%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthey%20(Kukis)%20are%20not%20the%20original%20inhabitants%20of%20Manipur%E2%80%9D.%20The%20Centre%20forwarded%20the%20representation%20to%20the%20state%20government%2C%20as%20the%20latter%E2%80%99s%20recommendation%20is%C2%A0a%20prerequisite%20to%20process%20any%20such%20proposal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESingh%20said%20that%20an%20all-tribe%20committee%20would%20be%20formed%20to%20decide%20whether%20the%20Chin%20Kuki%20community%20would%20be%20deleted%20from%20the%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20list%20of%20the%20state.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20were%20included%20in%20the%20(ST)%20list%20of%20Manipur%20but%20how%20they%20were%20included%20needs%20to%20be%20re-examined.%20Before%20commenting%2C%20we%20have%20to%20form%20a%20committee%20consisting%20of%20all%20tribes%20(of%20the%20state)%2C%E2%80%9D%20Singh%20told%20reporters%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2Fall-tribe-panel-to-be-formed-to-decide-if-chin-kukis-will-remain-st-manipur-cm%2Farticle67724832.ece%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20Press%20Trust%20of%20India%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKuki%20is%20a%20collective%20name%20of%20various%20tribes%20of%20Manipur%2C%20and%20Chin%20is%20one%20of%20those.%20The%20Chin%20community%20people%20also%20share%20ethnicity%20with%20the%20Mizos%20of%20Mizoram%20and%20a%20section%20of%20the%20residents%20of%20neighbouring%20Myanmar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20exception%20to%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20remarks%2C%20Indigenous%20Tribal%20Leaders%E2%80%99%20Forum%20(ITLF)%2C%20a%20Kuki-Zomi%20organisation%20based%20in%20Churachandpur%2C%20accused%20%E2%80%9Ccommunal%E2%80%9D%20Biren%20Singh%20of%20%E2%80%9Copening%20a%20new%20front%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20no%20secret%20that%20the%20state%20government%20in%20Manipur%2C%20controlled%20by%20the%20majority%20Meitei%20community%2C%20overtly%20and%20covertly%20supports%20the%20Meiteis%20in%20the%20current%20ethnic%20conflict.%20The%20communal%20Biren%20Singh%20administration%20has%20now%20opened%20a%20new%20front%20by%20pushing%20for%20the%20removal%20of%20the%20Kuki-Zo%20community%20from%20India%E2%80%99s%20ST%20list%2C%E2%80%9D%20read%20a%20statement%20issued%20by%20the%20ITLF%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAny%20further%20attempts%20by%20Biren%20Singh%20to%20use%20the%20state%20machinery%20to%20target%20the%20Kuki-Zo%20community%20will%20only%20escalate%20the%20conflict%2C%20which%20will%20ultimately%20be%20detrimental%20to%20him%20and%20the%20state%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20statement%20further%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKuki%20Inpi%2C%20the%20apex%20body%20of%20Kuki%20tribes%20in%20Manipur%2C%20called%20on%20the%20state%20government%20to%20stop%20any%20attempts%20to%20%E2%80%9Calter%20the%20ST%20status%20of%20the%20community%E2%80%9D%20immediately.%20%E2%80%9CKuki%20Inpi%20Sadar%20Hills%20vehemently%20condemns%20any%20attempt%20to%20erase%20the%20Kuki%20community%20from%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20status%2C%20as%20it%20blatantly%20violates%20the%20principles%20enshrined%20in%20the%20Indian%20Constitution.%20Such%20actions%20not%20only%20undermine%20the%20Constitutional%20safeguards%20provided%20to%20tribal%20communities%20but%20also%20perpetuate%20injustice%20and%20discrimination%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kuki%20Inpi%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManipur%20has%20been%20rocked%20by%20ethnic%20violence%20since%20May%20last%20year%20and%20over%20180%20people%20were%20killed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20violence%20erupted%20on%20May%203%20after%20a%20%E2%80%98Tribal%20Solidarity%20March%E2%80%99%20was%20organised%20in%20the%20hill%20districts%20to%20protest%20against%20the%20Meitei%20community%E2%80%99s%20demand%20for%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20(ST)%20status.%C2%A0Meiteis%20account%20for%20about%2053%25%20of%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20population%20and%20live%20mostly%20in%20the%20Imphal%20Valley%2C%20while%20tribals%2C%20which%20include%20Nagas%20and%20Kukis%2C%20constitute%2040%25%20and%20reside%20mainly%20in%20the%20hill%20districts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704966274000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F30163218%2FFwqAt6VXsAIGp1_.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fbiren-singh-opening-a-new-front-manipur-govts-possible-rethink-on-st-status-to-kukis-draws-ire%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Manipur%20chief%20minister%20said%20his%20government%20is%20considering%20setting%20up%20an%20all-tribe%20committee%20to%20decide%20if%20Kukis%20remain%20under%20Scheduled%20Tribes.%20Kuki%20outfits%20say%20the%20move%20would%20further%20escalate%20the%20ongoing%20conflict.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A21%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22htt