0is%20virtually%20omnipresent%2C%20to%20which%20everywhere%20is%20a%20national%20interest.%20The%20privileges%20of%20full%20spectrum%20dominance%20and%20forward%20power%20projection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20implications%20for%20President%20Biden%E2%80%99s%20re-election%20bid%20are%20increasingly%20bleak%20as%20national%20polls%20show%20Trump%20leading%20the%20incumbent%2C%20and%20as%20Arab%20and%20Muslim-Americans%20develop%20campaigns%20against%20the%20administration%E2%80%99s%20support%20for%20Israel%20and%20blocking%20of%20a%20ceasefire%20resolution%20at%20the%20United%20Nations.%20Though%20they%20are%20a%20very%20small%20minority%20of%20the%20US%20population%20and%20electorate%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthehill.com%2Fhomenews%2Fcampaign%2F4356645-arab-muslim-americans-could-abandon-biden-democrats-warn-advocates%2F%5C%22%3EMuslim-Americans%3C%2Fa%3E%20could%20tilt%20the%20balance%20of%20power%20within%20swing%20states%20towards%20Donald%20Trump.%20As%20ominously%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.brookings.edu%2Farticles%2Ffor-biden-youth-vote-polling-is-a-warning-not-the-apocalypse%2F%5C%22%3Evoters%20under%2035%20years%20of%20age%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20much%20larger%20slice%20of%20the%20electorate%2C%20who%20supported%20Biden%20by%20large%20margins%20in%202020%2C%20seem%20to%20be%20deserting%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F04%2F08132647%2Fdownload-3.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F04%2F08132647%2Fdownload-3.jpg%20800w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F04%2F08132647%2Fdownload-3-300x200.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-521330%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22533%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ETrump%20supporters%20marching%20on%20the%20US%20Capitol%20on%206%20January%202021.%20Photo%3A%20Wikimedia%20Commons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBut%20America%20remains%20great%E2%80%A6.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%20there%20remains%20an%20incontrovertible%20and%20fundamental%20fact%3A%20that%20while%20worldwide%20elections%20are%20important%2C%20their%20impacts%20are%20largely%20confined%20to%20specific%20regions%20or%20domains.%20The%20US%20election%2C%20however%2C%20is%20pivotal%20on%20all%20fronts%20%E2%80%93%20geoeconomically%2C%20geopolitically%2C%20politically%20%E2%80%93%20with%20worldwide%20ramifications.%20For%20all%20the%20talk%20of%20%E2%80%98decline%E2%80%99%20or%20the%20transition%20to%20multipolarity%2C%20the%20US%20remains%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20pivotal%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fundamental%20issues%20for%20the%20United%20States%20are%20domestically-rooted%20%E2%80%93%20in%20its%20politics%2C%20political%20system%2C%20and%20political%20economy.%20Factionalisation%20is%20the%20core%20political%20problem%3B%20a%20political%20party%20system%20deeply%20divided%2C%20political%20violence%20at%20enduringly%20high%20levels%2C%20an%20indicted%20GOP%20candidate%20leading%20a%20party%20uncommitted%20to%20free%20and%20fair%20elections%20and%20rules%20of%20the%20game%3B%20social%20and%20economic%20inequalities%2C%20and%20polarisations.%20And%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.americanprogress.org%2Farticle%2Fcorporate-capture-threatens-democratic-government%2F%5C%22%3Ecorporate%20dominance%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20both%20parties%20and%20their%20political-economic%20agendas%20remains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecent%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.harvard.edu%2Fgazette%2Fstory%2F2022%2F08%2Ftop-business-execs-more-polarized-than-nation-as-whole%2F%5C%22%3Eresearch%3C%2Fa%3E%20also%20shows%20that%20the%20top%20executives%20of%20major%20US%20corporations%20are%20leaning%20even%20more%20heavily%20toward%20the%20GOP%2C%20even%20as%20they%20mouth%20slogans%20about%20diversity%20and%20face%20accusations%20of%20%E2%80%9Cwokism%E2%80%9D%20from%20the%20Right.%20The%20corporate%20constituency%20behind%20a%20fascistic%20Trump-led%20political%20party%20has%20grown.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20reasons%20are%20not%20hard%20to%20find.%20When%20asked%20recently%20if%20he%20would%20be%20a%20dictator%20were%20he%20returned%20to%20the%20White%20House%2C%20Trump%20replied%20that%20he%20would%20be%20for%20just%20one%20day.%20On%20that%20day%2C%20he%20would%20close%20the%20borders%20and%2C%20very%20significantly%2C%20abolish%20government%20regulation%20of%20fossil%20fuel%20corporations.%20Racist%20divide%20and%20rule%20twinned%20with%20corporate%20freedom%20%E2%80%93%20the%20core%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fus-news%2F2023%2Fdec%2F06%2Fdonald-trump-sean-hannity-dictator-day-one-response-iowa-town-hall%5C%22%3ETrump%E2%80%99s%20political%20strategy%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fus-fascistic-violence-civil-war-election-2024%5C%22%3Etoxic%20recipe%20for%20political%20strife%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20violence%2C%20far-right%20and%20fascistic%20extremism%2C%20and%20state%20repression%20against%20popular%20resistance.%20Discussion%2C%20fearful%20and%20shocking%2C%20about%20fascism%20and%20civil%20war%20is%20now%20common%2C%20even%20if%20the%20mainstream%20media%20does%20not%20recognise%20it%2C%20as%20Bill%20Clinton%E2%80%99s%20labour%20secretary%20Robert%20Reich%2C%20recently%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fcommentisfree%2F2023%2Fdec%2F31%2Fmainstream-media-is-playing-into-trumps-neo-fascist-hands-im-sticking-with-democracy-and-the-guardian%5C%22%3Eclaimed%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBarbara%20F%20Walter%E2%80%99s%20important%20study%20%E2%80%93%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fbook-review-barbara-walter-america-civil-war-fascism%5C%22%3EHow%20Civil%20Wars%20Start%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%20(2022)%20%E2%80%93%20remains%20the%20key%20reference%20point%20with%20regard%20to%20the%20%E2%80%9Cfactionalisation%E2%80%9D%20process%20and%20the%20road%20to%20civil%20war%20and%20political%20violence%3A%20it%20remains%20relevant%20to%20understanding%20US%20politics%20today%20including%20the%20path%20to%20the%202024%20election%20and%20its%20ramifications%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECrises%20galore%20%E2%80%93%20poly%2C%20perma%2C%20organic%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20fundamental%20legitimacy%20crisis%20%E2%80%93%20a%20crisis%20of%20authority%20of%20the%20two%20main%20parties%20and%20their%20leaders%20%E2%80%93%20which%20remains%20the%20core%20underlying%20bedrock%20problem.%20It%20is%20the%20motherlode%20from%20which%20emanates%20all%20other%20schisms%20and%20faultlines.%20Call%20it%20what%20you%20will%20and%20from%20whichever%20part%20of%20the%20ideological%20spectrum%20%E2%80%93%20poly%20crisis%2C%20perma%20crisis%2C%20organic%20crisis%20%E2%80%93%20crisis%20is%20now%20part%20of%20the%20lexicon%20of%20our%20times.%20The%20new%20normal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20crisis%20has%20a%20face%20%E2%80%93%20two%20faces%2C%20actually%2C%20as%20exemplified%20by%20the%20two%20likely%20main%20contenders%20for%20the%20US%20presidency%3A%20Donald%20Trump%20and%20Joseph%20Biden%2C%20in%20a%20country%20seen%20by%20the%20majority%20of%20voters%20as%20heading%20in%20the%20wrong%20direction.%20Trump%E2%80%99s%20age%2C%20criminal%20indictments%20(and%20two%20impeachments)%20and%20march%20towards%20American-style%20fascism%3B%20and%20Biden%E2%80%99s%20age%20and%20health%2C%20and%20foot-dragging%20on%20indictments%20of%20Trump%20since%202021.%20Major%20complicating%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20mere%20eight%20swing%20states%20may%20determine%20the%20election%20outcome%20%E2%80%93%20Arizona%2C%20Michigan%2C%20Georgia%2C%20Wisconsin%2C%20Pennsylvania%2C%20New%20Hampshire%2C%20and%20North%20Carolina%20%E2%80%93%20another%20tight%20race%20between%20two%20unpopular%20candidates.%20If%20there%20were%20such%20a%20choice%20in%202024%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FNone_of_the_above%5C%22%3ENone%20of%20the%20Above%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20would%20win%20the%20election.%20The%20lesser%20of%20two%20evils%20or%20the%20evil%20of%20two%20lessers%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Trump%E2%80%99s%20name%20on%20ballots%20in%20several%20states%20is%20in%20jeopardy%20or%20removed.%20The%20matter%20will%20end%20up%20at%20the%20door%20of%20the%20right-wing%20majority%20US%20Supreme%20Court.%20Another%20first%20for%20Donald%20Trump.%20Whichever%20way%20the%20chips%20fall%20%E2%80%93%20most%20likely%20towards%20Trump%20and%20his%20incensed%20fan%20base%20%E2%80%93%20political%20peace%20is%20unlikely%20to%20prevail%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fwill-the-sc-rule-in-trumps-favour-to-keep-his-presidential-ambitions-alive%5C%22%3EWill%20the%20SC%20Rule%20in%20Trump%E2%80%99s%20Favour%20to%20Keep%20His%20Presidential%20Ambitions%20Alive%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20will%20need%20to%20keep%20an%20eye%20on%20setting%20a%20precedent%20when%20it%20rules%20on%20barring%20Trump%20from%20the%202024%20election.%20If%20Trump%20is%20ruled%20to%20be%20exempt%20from%20the%2014%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Amendment%E2%80%99s%20Article%203%2C%20which%20bars%20insurrectionists%20from%20holding%20office%20if%20they%20have%20taken%20an%20oath%20to%20protect%20and%20uphold%20the%20Constitution%2C%20there%20would%20be%20wider%20ramifications.%20The%20right-wing%20majority%20Supreme%20Court%20would%20also%20be%20giving%20virtual%20carte%20blanche%20to%20any%20future%20president%20of%20a%20political%20persuasion%20uncongenial%20to%20the%20GOP%20to%20refuse%20to%20leave%20office%20following%20electoral%20defeat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%20laughable%20the%20notion%20that%20a%20US%20president%20is%20not%20an%20officer%20of%20the%20United%20States%2C%20this%20is%20the%20main%20plank%20of%20Trump%E2%80%99s%20case.%20And%20the%20claim%20that%20barring%20him%20for%20insurrection%20is%20anti-democratic%20reinforces%20the%20upside%20down%20logics%20of%20American%20political%20culture%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWill%20there%20be%20a%20peaceful%20transfer%20of%20power%3F%20There%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20one%20in%202020.%20Thousands%20of%20politically%20vetted%20national%20guard%20were%20on%20duty%20during%20Biden%E2%80%99s%20inauguration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECould%20the%20US%20break%20up%20along%20political%20lines%20with%20some%20states%20accepting%20and%20others%20rejecting%20the%20outcome%3F%20Who%20knows%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20these%20questions%20are%20being%20asked%20at%20all%20is%20an%20indication%20of%20the%20new%20reality%20of%20the%20US%20and%20therefore%20global%20political%20life%2C%20of%20the%20global%20disorder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fiparmar%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EInderjeet%20Parmar%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20is%20a%20professor%20of%20international%20politics%20and%20associate%20dean%20of%20research%20in%20the%20School%20of%20Policy%20and%20Global%20Affairs%20at%20City%2C%20University%20of%20London%2C%20a%20fellow%20of%20the%20Academy%20of%20Social%20Sciences%2C%20and%20a%20columnist%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3EThe%20Wire%3Cem%3E.%20He%20is%20an%20International%20Fellow%20at%20the%20ROADS%20Initiative%20think%20tank%2C%20Islamabad%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3Eand%20author%20of%20several%20books%20including%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3EFoundations%20of%20the%20American%20Century%3Cem%3E.%20He%20is%20currently%20writing%20a%20book%20on%20the%20history%2C%20politics%2C%20and%20powers%20of%20the%20US%20Foreign%20Policy%20Establishment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704963601000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F11140034%2FEffect-61.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fas-the-us-enters-election-year-will-there-be-a-peaceful-transfer-of-power%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22There%20is%20a%20deep%20sense%20of%20foreboding%20in%20the%20US%20as%20the%20implications%20for%20President%20Biden's%20re-election%20bid%20are%20increasingly%20bleak%20as%20national%20polls%20show%20Trump%20leading%20the%20incumbent.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fas-the-us-enters-election-year-will-there-be-a-peaceful-transfer-of-power%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Rs%2010%2C000%20Crores'%3A%20In%20a%20Poll%20Year%2C%20a%20PDS%20Scam%20Once%20Again%20Poses%20Corruption%20Hurdle%20for%20TMC%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F11135848%2FUntitled-design-10-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EKolkata%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EOn%20January%208%20(Monday)%2C%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20alleged%20extensive%20corruption%20within%20the%20West%20Bengal%20public%20distribution%20system%20(PDS)%20scam.%20ED%20sources%20estimated%20that%20a%20single%20suspect%2C%20Shankar%20Adhya%2C%20the%20former%20chairman%20of%20Bongaon%20Municipality%20and%20a%20close%20aide%20of%20the%20arrested%20minister%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindubusinessline.com%2Fnews%2Fed-arrests-west-bengal-minister-jyotipriya-mullick-in-pds-irregularities-case%2Farticle67467231.ece%5C%22%3EJyotipriya%20Mallick%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20could%20be%20responsible%20for%20embezzling%20up%20to%20Rs%2010%2C000%20crores.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20the%20critical%20general%20election%20approaches%2C%20the%20ration%20scam%2C%20involving%20thousands%20of%20crores%2C%20adds%20to%20the%20embarrassment%20for%20chief%20minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20and%20senior%20TMC%20leaders.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2Fmagnitude-of-the-10000-crore-pds-scam-in-west-bengal-is-enormous-ed%2Farticle67720001.ece%5C%22%3EED%20submissions%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Adhya%20played%20a%20direct%20role%20in%20laundering%20approximately%20Rs%2010%2C000%20crores%20through%20foreign%20currency%20trading%20and%20exchange%20in%20the%20border%20areas%20of%20the%20state%2C%20with%20nearly%20half%20of%20that%20sum%20stemming%20from%20the%20ration%20distribution%20scam.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20The%20agency%20claimed%20in%20court%20that%20Adhya%20managed%20to%20smuggle%20out%20over%20Rs%202%2C500%20crores%20to%20Dubai%20through%20forex%20trade.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fkolkata%2Fday-after-attack-on-ed-officials-hunt-begins-for-tmc-leader-sheikh-shahjahan%2Farticleshow%2F106603062.cms%5C%22%3ESheikh%20Shahjahan%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20other%20key%20suspect%2C%20remains%20at%20large%20despite%20an%20ED%20look-out%20circular%20(LOC)%20issued%20for%20him.%20The%20LOC%20was%20issued%20after%20an%20armed%20mob%20attacked%20investigating%20agencies%20during%20a%20raid%20in%20Sandeshkhali%2C%20North%2024%20Parganas%2C%20last%20Friday%20(January%205).%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EWhat%20is%20the%20ration%20scam%20in%20West%20Bengal%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDuring%20the%20COVID-19%20lockdown%20in%20May%202020%2C%20protests%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fkolkata%2Faccused-of-irregularities-in-pds-ration-dealers-house-ransacked-in-murshidabad-6391017%2F%5C%22%3Eerupted%20in%20West%20Bengal%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20alleged%20irregularities%20in%20the%20distribution%20of%20PDS%20grains.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20first%20information%20report%20(FIR)%20was%20filed%20in%20Nadia%20district.%20Then-governor%20of%20West%20Bengal%20Jagdeep%20Dhankhar%20(now%20vice%20president)%2C%20and%20the%20central%20government%20had%20criticised%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20handling%20of%20the%20PDS.%20On%20April%2023%2C%202020%2C%20the%20Centre%20informed%20the%20state%20that%20food%20grain%20distribution%20was%20non-existent%20under%20the%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Garib%20Kalyan%20Anna%20Yojana%20(PMGKAY).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fin-bengals-sandeshkhali-controversial-tmc-leader-sheikh-shahjahans-hold-is-powerful%5C%22%3E%20In%20Bengal%E2%80%99s%20Sandeshkhali%2C%20Controversial%20TMC%20Leader%20Sheikh%20Shahjahan%E2%80%99s%20Hold%20Is%20Powerful%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fexplained%2Fed-crpf-attacked-west-bengal-pds-scam-9098098%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20under%20PMGKAY%2C%20each%20ration%20card%20holder%20was%20entitled%20to%205%20kilogram%20of%20food%20grains%20and%201%20kg%20of%20pulses%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20the%20monthly%20quota%20of%205%20kg%20of%20subsidised%20food%20grains%20per%20person%20under%20the%20National%20Food%20Security%20Act%20(NFSA).%20Investigations%20revealed%20that%20an%20influential%20businessman%2C%20Bakibur%20Rahman%2C%20supplied%20rice%20and%20wheat%20in%20insufficient%20quantities%20to%20fair%20price%20shop%20distributors.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBakibur%2C%20allegedly%20supported%20by%20Mallick%2C%20a%20powerful%20minister%20close%20to%20the%20chief%20minister%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eprofited%20by%20selling%20the%20excess%20grain%20in%20the%20open%20market.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EED%20sources%20claim%20that%20flour%20mill%20owners%20supplied%20less%20flour%20to%20distributors%20than%20paid%20for%20by%20the%20government.%20Mill%20owners%20claimed%20that%20for%20the%20price%20of%201%20kg%20of%20flour%2C%20government%20suppliers%20received%20only%20about%20600%20grams.%20Approximately%2030%25%20of%20the%20PDS%20ration%20intended%20for%20beneficiaries%20in%20West%20Bengal%20was%20redirected%20to%20the%20open%20market.%20In%20collaboration%20with%20some%20local%20leaders%20from%20the%20ruling%20party%2C%20rice%20millers%20created%20fake%20bank%20accounts%20for%20farmers%2C%20siphoning%20off%20the%20minimum%20support%20price%20(MSP)%20earmarked%20for%20paddy%20growers.%20Rice%20millers%20earned%20nearly%20Rs%20200%20per%20quintal%20for%20grains%20that%20government%20agencies%20were%20supposed%20to%20procure%20at%20MSP%20from%20farmers%2C%20of%20which%2C%20a%20significant%20percentage%20had%20allegedly%20to%20be%20shared%20with%20Mallick%2C%20who%20oversaw%20the%20Food%20and%20Supplies%20Ministry%20in%20the%20previous%20TMC%20government%20from%202016%20to%202021.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fpartha-chatterjee-ssc-scam-tmc-manata-corruption%5C%22%3EPartha%20Chatterjee%2C%20another%20major%20leader%20currently%20in%20jail%2C%20had%20to%20lose%20his%20portfolio%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20his%20involvement%20in%20the%20job%20recruitment%20scam%20came%20to%20light%2C%20Mallick%20continues%20to%20remain%20a%20minister%20holding%20key%20position%20in%20the%20cabinet.%20Similarly%2C%20Shahjahan%20and%20Adhya%2C%20crucial%20figures%20in%20TMC%E2%80%99s%20electoral%20strategy%20in%20North%2024%20Parganas%2C%20continue%20to%20enjoy%20party%20support%20despite%20being%20confronted%20with%20accusations%20spanning%20from%20financial%20misconduct%20to%20homicide.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERecently%2C%20Shovandev%20Chattopadhyay%2C%20a%20seasoned%20TMC%20leader%2C%20cautioned%20that%20ED%20officials%20can%20anticipate%20similar%20resistance%20from%20TMC%20student%20activists%20in%20the%20days%20ahead%2C%20leading%20to%20public%20outcry.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDuring%20the%20panchayat%20elections%20in%202013%2C%202018%2C%20and%202023%2C%20opposition%20parties%20struggled%20to%20field%20candidates%20in%20the%20Sadeshkhali%20blocks%2C%20where%20Shahjahan%20wields%20significant%20political%20influence.%20Likewise%2C%20Adhya%E2%80%99s%20influence%20in%20the%20Matua-dominated%20border%20areas%20near%20Bangaon%20became%20evident%20when%20ED%20officials%20encountered%20resistance%20from%20his%20supporters.%20Following%20his%20arrest%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Emany%20locals%20came%20forward%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fer-tmc-councillor-said-in-bangaon-985709.html%5C%22%3Edisclosed%3C%2Fa%3E%20his%20involvement%20in%20corruption%2C%20intimidation%2C%20and%20violence%20to%20the%20local%20media%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20corruption%20in%20ration%20distribution%20poses%20a%20threat%20to%20the%20TMC%20organisation%20as%20there%20are%20tens%20of%20Shahjahan%20within%20the%20party.%20Their%20potential%20arrests%20could%20exert%20pressure%20on%20the%20party%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20cascading%20effect%20on%20its%20influence%2C%E2%80%9D%20observed%20political%20analyst%20Biswanath%20Chakraborty.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fpartha-chatterjee-ssc-scam-tmc-manata-corruption%5C%22%3ETMC%20May%20Have%20Sacked%20Partha%20Chatterjee%2C%20But%20Its%20Problems%20With%20Corruption%20Run%20Deep%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20part%20of%20the%20collusion%2C%20ration%20dealers%20were%20compelled%20to%20contribute%20a%20portion%20of%20their%20monthly%20earnings%20to%20the%20local%20syndicate%20in%20exchange%20for%20the%20windfall.%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20spoke%20to%20a%20ration%20dealer%20in%20Murshidabad%2C%20whose%20identity%20is%20being%20withheld%20for%20protection.%20The%20dealer%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20amount%20of%20money%20we%E2%80%99re%20paying%20as%20bribe%20and%20commission%20to%20the%20local%20syndicate%20kept%20on%20increasing.%20Many%20of%20us%20felt%20the%20dealership%20was%20not%20profitable%20anymore.%20I%20applied%20three%20years%20back%20to%20return%20my%20licence%2C%20but%20it%20was%20not%20accepted.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20a%20family%20of%20five%2C%20each%20with%20ration%20cards.%20Yet%2C%20we%20receive%20only%2012%20kgs%20of%20rice%20every%20month%20from%20the%20ration%20shop.%20I%20use%20ration%20cards%20from%20other%20families%20who%20do%20not%20want%20to%20eat%20this%20rice%2C%20but%20are%20eligible%20for%20rations.%20I%20pay%20them%20Rs%2025%20per%20kg%20for%20their%20share%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Tapan%20Roy%2C%20a%20part-time%20transport%20worker%20from%20Dhupguri%20in%20North%20Bengal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202007%2C%20during%20the%20tenure%20of%20the%20Buddhadeb%20Bhattacharjee-led%20Left%20Front%20government%2C%20protests%20erupted%20over%20alleged%20irregularities%20in%20the%20public%20distribution%20system.%20One%20of%20the%20demonstrations%2C%20marked%20by%20violence%2C%20resulted%20in%20the%20death%20of%20Ayub%20Sheikh%2C%20a%20protester%2C%20in%20a%20clash%20with%20the%20police.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20recently%20visited%20Ayub%E2%80%99s%20family%2C%20who%20now%20claim%20to%20have%20received%20insufficient%20rations.%20Jhunafa%20Bibi%2C%20Ayub%E2%80%99s%20wife%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CSometimes%20the%20rice%20arrives%20in%20a%20month%2C%20sometimes%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t.%20Kerosene%20is%20unavailable.%20Previously%2C%20lentils%20were%20accessible%3B%20now%20there%20are%20none.%20Wheat%20flour%20arrives%20irregularly%2C%20and%20the%20quality%20is%20very%20poor!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETranslated%20from%20Bangla%20to%20English%20by%20Aparna%20Bhattacharya.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704963057000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F11135848%2FUntitled-design-10-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Frs-10000-crores-in-a-poll-year-a-pds-scam-once-again-poses-corruption-hurdle-for-tmc%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20the%20critical%20general%20election%20approaches%2C%20the%20situation%2C%20involving%20thousands%20of%20crores%2C%20adds%20to%20the%20embarrassment%20for%20chief%20minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20and%20senior%20TMC%20leaders.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Frs-10000-crores-in-a-poll-year-a-pds-scam-once-again-poses-corruption-hurdle-for-tmc%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22As%20a%20Classical%20Musician%2C%20Rashid%20Khan%20Showed%20His%20Brilliance%20at%20a%20Very%20Young%20Age%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F11130712%2FUntitled-design-9-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EUstad%20Rashid%20Khan%20was%20the%20great%20grandson%20of%20Rampur-Sehaswan%20Gharana%20founder%20Enayat%20Hussain%20Khan.%20He%20did%20his%20lineage%20proud.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGone%20too%20soon%20at%2055%2C%20when%20some%20musicians%20reach%20a%20plateau%2C%20he%20could%20have%20continued%20to%20evolve%20because%20of%20his%20fertile%20mind.%20The%20coming%20together%20of%20voice%2C%20style%2C%20fluid%20%3Cem%3Etaans%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20reposeful%20%3Cem%3Eaalaap%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20made%20him%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fthe-arts%2Fustad-rashid-khan-murad-ali-tribute%5C%22%3Erare%20and%20complete%20musician%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20lacked%20nothing%20in%20any%20area%20of%20his%20field%20and%20beyond%2C%20as%20he%20even%20ventured%20into%20film%20music.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20knew%20Rashid%20from%20my%20two%20years%20tenure%20at%20Sangeet%20Research%20Academy%2C%20where%20we%20were%20both%20%E2%80%98scholars%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20the%20term%20for%20scholarship%20holders%20%E2%80%93%20he%20under%20Ustad%20Nisar%20Hussain%20Khan%20and%20I%20under%20Pandita%20Girija%20Devi%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E.%20SRA%20carries%20forward%20the%20%3Cem%3Eguru-shishya%20parampara%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%93%20the%20tradition%20of%20teacher%20and%20student%20relationships.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20as%20a%20%E2%80%98scholar%E2%80%99%2C%20he%20was%20considered%20a%20maestro%20by%20the%20gurus%20at%20SRA%20%E2%80%93%20Pandit%20A.%20Kanan%20who%20represented%20Kirana%20Gharana%E2%80%99s%20reposeful%20style%20and%20who%20I%20loved%20because%20he%20had%20a%20huge%20photograph%20of%20my%20Guru%20Begum%20Akhtar%20at%20the%20very%20entrance%20of%20his%20home%3B%20his%20wife%20Malavika%20Kanan%2C%20who%20said%20she%20never%20read%20any%20newspaper%20in%20the%20morning%20because%20all%20the%20bad%20news%20ruined%20her%20day%3B%20the%20stern-faced%20Ustad%20Nisar%20Hussain%20Khan%2C%20Rashid%E2%80%99s%20mentor%20and%20guru%2C%20a%20man%20of%20few%20words%20and%20an%20uncompromising%20demeanour%3B%20Pandit%20Jagdish%20Prasad%20whose%20wife%20would%20complain%20unabashedly%20that%20he%20kept%20her%20awake%20all%20night%3B%20Pandit%20Sunil%20Bose%20and%20Pandit%20Ajoy%20Chakraborty%20who%20was%20then%20a%20scholar-musician.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVijay%20Kichlu%20was%20at%20the%20helm%20of%20affairs%20as%20the%20director%20of%20SRA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20jointly%20mentored%20and%20assessed%20each%20%E2%80%98scholar%E2%80%99%20once%20a%20week.%20About%20Rashid%2C%20they%20would%20say%20amongst%20themselves%2C%20%E2%80%9CWho%20are%20we%20to%20assess%20him%3F%20He%E2%80%99s%20our%20equal%2C%20not%20less%20than%20us%E2%80%9D.%20They%20too%20were%20in%20awe%20of%20his%20brilliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20used%20to%20come%20over%20in%20the%20evenings%20to%20Girija%20Devi%20or%20%3Cem%3EAppa%20ji%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98s%20house%20often%2C%20and%20would%20regale%20us%20with%20his%20mimicry.%20He%20used%20to%20do%20a%20hilarious%20Bharatnatyam%20%3Cem%3Ebhav-dikhana%3C%2Fem%3E%20act%20of%20a%20famous%20dancer%20and%20would%20have%20us%20all%20in%20splits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20he%20had%20fallen%20madly%20in%20love%20with%20the%20woman%20who%20he%20eventually%20married%2C%20and%20was%20tortured%20by%20his%20guru%20%E2%80%98s%20command%20to%20marry%20his%20relative%20instead.%20At%20that%20time%2C%20I%20was%20his%20confidant.%20He%20would%20speak%20to%20me%20of%20his%20despair%20and%20complained%20bitterly%20that%20his%20guru%20would%20order%20him%20to%20run%20errands%20all%20morning%20when%20he%20wanted%20to%20do%20practice%20music%20instead.%20We%20shared%20grouses%20against%20our%20gurus%20and%20felt%20we%20were%20at%20their%20mercy.%20I%20found%20my%20guru%20unkind%20as%20I%20constantly%20compared%20her%20with%20my%20first%20guru%2C%20Begum%20Akhtar%2C%20who%20was%20extremely%20indulgent.%20Later%2C%20I%20loved%20Girija%20Devi%20too%2C%20as%20I%20am%20sure%20Rashid%20also%20came%20to%20love%20his%20guru.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERashid%20and%20I%20met%20backstage%20before%20one%20of%20his%20concerts%20some%20years%20later%20and%20he%20chided%20me%3A%20%E2%80%9CLook%20where%20I%20have%20reached%E2%80%A6why%20aren%E2%80%99t%20you%20better%20known%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20music%20shone%20through%20his%20profound%20honesty%2C%20which%20was%20reflected%20in%20his%20gaze%20towards%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHere%20are%20four%20renditions%20by%20Rashid%20Khan%20chosen%20by%20Rekha%20Surya%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fshare%2Fr%2FpJMRHRid9G2b61RY%2F%3Fmibextid%3Dqi2Omg%5C%22%3E1%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fshare%2Fr%2FDPsz6ALK8dLBecVC%2F%3Fmibextid%3Dqi2Omg%5C%22%3E2%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fshare%2Fr%2F1Wihd34o1zkFraTe%2F%3Fmibextid