Cem%3Ekari%20dosa%20%3C%2Fem%3Eplace%2C%20which%20she%20craved.%20So%20when%20she%20thought%20of%20serving%20something%20that%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20easily%20available%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20she%20thought%20of%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EKari%20dosa%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20traditionally%20made%20with%20mutton%20kheema%2C%20originated%20in%20Madurai%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20worked%20on%20perfecting%20the%20recipes%20and%20tastes%20for%20two%20months%20before%20launching%20her%20food%20cart%20in%20J%20P%20Nagar%2C%20Bengaluru.%20Initially%2C%20her%20family%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20in%20favour%20of%20her%20starting%20this%20food%20enterprise%20that%20requires%20physical%20labour%20and%20standing%20for%20long%20periods%20of%20time%2C%20but%20she%20was%20resolute.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20to%20create%20my%20own%20brand%20and%20achieve%20something.%20I%20wanted%20to%20push%20my%20limits%20and%20do%20something%20new%20every%20day.%20If%20I%20could%20do%20a%20desk%20job%20for%20eight%20hours%20daily%2C%20why%20can%E2%80%99t%20I%20stand%20for%20four%20hours%3F%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20a%20cushy%20job%20in%20an%20air-conditioned%20office%2C%20Veena%20now%20slogs%20it%20out%20on%20the%20streets%20of%20Bengaluru%2C%20in%20the%20hugely%20competitive%20street%20food%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20starts%20her%20day%20at%204%3A30%20am%20every%20day%20and%20sells%20%3Cem%3Ekari%20dosas%3C%2Fem%3E%20made%20with%20chicken%3Cem%3E%20kheema%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20prawn%20%3Cem%3Ethokku%20%3C%2Fem%3E(curry)%20and%20mutton%3Cem%3E%20kheema%3C%2Fem%3E.%20A%20plain%20%3Cem%3Edosa%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20priced%20at%20Rs%2010%2C%20while%20the%20mutton%20%3Cem%3Ekari%20dosa%3C%2Fem%3E%20costs%20Rs%20150.%20The%20stall%20is%20open%20from%207%3A30%20am%20to%2011%3A30%20am.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVeena%20managed%20to%20eventually%20convince%20her%20family.%20She%20says%20her%20husband%2C%20a%20fitness%20trainer%20by%20profession%2C%20is%20her%20biggest%20